String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("u1") Dim sTimePeriod As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("TimePeriod","") ' Accounts Dim sAccount As String = "Total_Phased_Commitment, Total_Phased_Obligation, Phased_Commitment_UFR, Phased_Obligation_UFR" Dim lAccount As List(Of String) = sAccount.Split(", ").Select(Function(item)item.Trim()).ToList() Dim sAccounSql As String = "REQ_ID,REQ_Rqmt_Status,REQ_Title,REQ_Description,REQ_Attachments_Ind,REQ_Related_Request,REQ_Recurring_Justification,REQ_Impact_If_Not_Funded,REQ_Risk_If_Not_Funded,REQ_Cost_Methodology_Cmt,REQ_Cost_Growth_Justification,REQ_Must_Fund,REQ_Requested_Fund_Source,REQ_Army_initiative_Directive,REQ_Command_Initiative_Directive,REQ_Activity_Exercise,REQ_IT_Cyber_Rqmt_Ind,REQ_UIC_Acct,REQ_Flex_Field_1,REQ_Flex_Field_2,REQ_Flex_Field_3,REQ_Flex_Field_4,REQ_Flex_Field_5,REQ_New_Rqmt_Ind,REQ_CPA_Ind,REQ_PBR_Submission,REQ_UPL_Submission,REQ_Contract_Number,REQ_Task_Order_Number,REQ_Target_Date_Of_Award,REQ_POP_Expiration_Date,REQ_FTE_CME,REQ_COR_Email,REQ_POC_Email,REQ_Directorate,REQ_Division,REQ_Branch,REQ_Rev_POC_Email,REQ_MDEP_Func_Email,REQ_Notification_Email_List,REQ_Comments,REQ_Creator_Name,REQ_Creation_Date_Time,REQ_Last_Updated_Name,REQ_Last_Updated_Date,REQ_Status_History" Dim lAccountSql As List(Of String) = sAccounSql.Split(", ").Select(Function(item)item.Trim()).ToList() ' Get file name args Dim sTemplate As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("Template","") Dim sFvParam As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("FvParam","") Dim sFilePath As String = "" BRApi.Dashboards.Parameters.SetLiteralParameterValue(si,False,sFvParam,sFilePath)
' Throw new exception if FC or APPN is not selected If String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(sFundCenter) Or String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(u1) Then Throw New Exception("Please select a funds center and appropriation to export package details.") End If
' Data table that stores information for export Dim dtAll As New DataTable
' If no fund center is passed then stop If String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(sFundCenter) Or String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(sAccount) Then Return dtAll End If
' If the fund center passed is not a descendent of the WF then stop Dim mbrScrpt As String = "E#" & sCube & ".DescendantsInclusive.Where(Name Contains " & sFundCenter.Replace("_General","") & ")" Dim lCubeMembers As List (Of MemberInfo) = BRApi.Finance.Metadata.GetMembersUsingFilter(si, "E_" & sCube, mbrScrpt, True )
If Not lCubeMembers.Count > 0 Then Return dtAll End If
'--------- get Entity Text3 --------- Dim entityMem As Member = BRApi.Finance.Metadata.GetMember(si, DimType.Entity.Id, sFundCenter).Member Dim wfScenarioTypeID As Integer = BRApi.Finance.Scenario.GetScenarioType(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey).Id Dim wfTime As String = BRApi.Finance.Time.GetNameFromId(si,si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) Dim wfTimeId As Integer = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si,DimType.Time.Id,wfTime) Dim entityText3 As String = BRApi.Finance.Entity.Text(si, entityMem.MemberId, 3, wfScenarioTypeID, wfTimeId) entityText3 = entityText3.Substring(entityText3.Length -2, 2)
'--------- get next workflow level --------- Dim currentStatus As String = entityText3.Substring(1,1) Dim iCurrentLevel As Integer = CInt(currentStatus) Dim iNextLevel As Integer = iCurrentLevel - 1 Dim currentWFLevel As String = "L" & iCurrentLevel Dim newWFLevel As String = "L" & iNextLevel
'--------- derive FC List ---------- sFundCenter = sFundCenter.ToLower.Replace("_general","") Dim entityPk = BRApi.Finance.Dim.GetDimPk(si, "E_" & sCube) Dim nAncestorID As Integer = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si, DimType.Entity.Id, sCube) Dim nBaseID As Integer = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si, DimType.Entity.Id, sFundCenter) Dim isBase As Boolean = BRApi.Finance.Members.IsBase(si,entityPk, nAncestorID, nBaseID) Dim lEntity As New List(Of String) Dim entitySQL As String = "" If isBase = True Then entitySQL = $"('{sFundCenter}')" lEntity.Add(sFundCenter) Else Dim lFundCenters As List(Of MemberInfo) = BRApi.Finance.Metadata.GetMembersUsingFilter(si, "E_" & sCube, "E#"& sFundCenter &".Base",True) Dim isFirst As Boolean = True For Each FC As MemberInfo In lFundCenters If isFirst Then entitySQL &= $"('{FC.Member.Name}')" Else entitySQL &= $", ('{FC.Member.Name}')" End If isFirst = False lEntity.Add(FC.Member.Name) Next End If '--------- derive status ---------- Dim statusSQL As String = $"'{currentWFLevel}%'" Dim SQL As New Text.StringBuilder 'New SQL.AppendLine($"If object_id('tempdb..#PivotedDetails') is not null drop Table #PivotedDetails; ") SQL.AppendLine($"If object_id('tempdb..#FilteredDataRecords') is not null drop Table #FilteredDataRecords; ") SQL.AppendLine($" ") SQL.AppendLine($"Select ") SQL.AppendLine($" SCENARIO, ") SQL.AppendLine($" ENTITY, ") SQL.AppendLine($" FLOW, ") Dim i As Integer = 1 For Each Account As String In lAccountSql If i = lAccountSql.Count Then SQL.AppendLine($" MAX(Case When ACCOUNT = '{Account}' THEN TEXT END) AS '{Account}' ") Else SQL.AppendLine($" MAX(Case When ACCOUNT = '{Account}' THEN TEXT END) AS '{Account}', ") End If i+=1 Next SQL.AppendLine($" Into #PivotedDetails ") SQL.AppendLine($"From ") SQL.AppendLine($" DATAATTACHMENT ") SQL.AppendLine($" Join (VALUES {entitySQL}) AS ENTITY_LIST(VALUE) ON DATAATTACHMENT.ENTITY = ENTITY_LIST.VALUE ") SQL.AppendLine($"Where ") SQL.AppendLine($" CUBE = '{sCube}' ") SQL.AppendLine($" And SCENARIO = '{sScenario}' ") SQL.AppendLine($"Group By ") SQL.AppendLine($" SCENARIO, ENTITY, FLOW") ' SQL.AppendLine($" HAVING MAX(Case When ACCOUNT = 'REQ_RQMT_STATUS' THEN TEXT END) Like {statusSQL} ")
SQL.AppendLine($"; ") SQL.AppendLine($"Select ") SQL.AppendLine($" SCENARIO, ") SQL.AppendLine($" ENTITY AS 'Funds Ctr', ") SQL.AppendLine($" FLOW AS 'REQ', ") SQL.AppendLine($" '' AS FUND, ") SQL.AppendLine($" ' ' AS MDEP, ") SQL.AppendLine($" ' ' AS APEPT, ") SQL.AppendLine($" ' ' AS 'DollarType', ") SQL.AppendLine($" ' ' AS 'Cost Cat', ") SQL.AppendLine($" '""' + REQ_Title + '""', ") SQL.AppendLine($" REQ_Rqmt_Status, ") For Each Acct As String In lAccount ' SQL.AppendLine($" 0 As '{Acct}', ") 'original SQL.AppendLine($" CAST(0 As BIGINT) '{Acct}', ") 'used to handle large value greater then billions ' SQL.AppendLine($" 0 As '{Acct} Carryover', ") Next lAccountSql.Remove("REQ_Title") lAccountSql.Remove("REQ_Rqmt_Status") i = 1 For Each Account As String In lAccountSql If i = lAccountSql.Count Then SQL.AppendLine($" '""' + [{Account}] + '""'" ) Else SQL.AppendLine($" '""' + [{Account}] + '""'," ) End If i+=1 Next SQL.AppendLine($"From ") SQL.AppendLine($" #PivotedDetails") SQL.AppendLine($"Order By ") SQL.AppendLine($" ENTITY, ") SQL.AppendLine($" FLOW ")
'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "SQL: " & SQL.ToString) 'Dim dtFetch As New DataTable
Using dbConn As DbConnInfo = BRApi.Database.CreateApplicationDbConnInfo(si) dtAll = BRApi.Database.ExecuteSql(dbConn,SQL.ToString(),True) End Using 'Return dtAll For Each column As DataColumn In dtAll.Columns column.ReadOnly = False If column.ColumnName = "FUND" Or column.ColumnName = "MDEP" Or column.ColumnName = "APEPT" Or column.ColumnName = "DollarType" Or column.ColumnName = "Cost Cat" Then column.MaxLength = 100 Next 'For loop used to retrieve the total amounts for Commitment, Obligation, CommitmentUFR , Obligation UFR For Each FundCenter As String In lEntity For Each Acct As String In lAccount 'DataUnitPK - GetDataBufferCell to grab total amount at the current FY Dim myDataUnitPkAccountTotal As New DataUnitPk( _ BRApi.Finance.Cubes.GetCubeInfo(si, sCube).Cube.CubeId, _ BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si, dimTypeId.Entity, FundCenter ), _ BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si, dimTypeId.Entity, ""), _ DimConstants.Local, _ BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si, dimTypeId.Scenario, sScenario), BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si, dimTypeId.Time, sBUDTime)) 'Buffer coordinates. 'DataBufferCellPK Dim myDbCellPkAccountTotal As New DataBufferCellPk( DimConstants.All ) myDbCellPkAccountTotal.AccountId = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si, dimTypeId.Account, Acct) myDbCellPkAccountTotal.OriginId = DimConstants.BeforeAdj myDbCellPkAccountTotal.ICId = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si, dimTypeId.Entity, FundCenter) myDbCellPkAccountTotal.UD5Id = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si, dimTypeId.UD5, "None") myDbCellPkAccountTotal.UD7Id = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si, dimTypeId.UD7, "None") myDbCellPkAccountTotal.UD8Id = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si, dimTypeId.UD8, "None")
Dim lTotalAccountAmounts As List(Of DataCell) = BRApi.Finance.Data.GetDataBufferDataCells(si, myDataUnitPkAccountTotal, dimConstants.Periodic, myDbCellPkAccountTotal, True, True)
'DataUnitPK - GetDataBufferCell to grab total carryover amount at (FY + 1)M12 Dim myDataUnitPkCarryoverTotal As New DataUnitPk( _ BRApi.Finance.Cubes.GetCubeInfo(si, sCube).Cube.CubeId, _ BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si, dimTypeId.Entity, FundCenter ), _ BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si, dimTypeId.Entity, ""), _ DimConstants.Local, _ BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si, dimTypeId.Scenario, sScenario), BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si, dimTypeId.Time, sCarryoverYrM12)) 'Buffer coordinates. 'DataBufferCellPK Dim myDbCellPkCarryoverTotal As New DataBufferCellPk( DimConstants.All ) myDbCellPkCarryoverTotal.AccountId = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si, dimTypeId.Account, Acct) myDbCellPkCarryoverTotal.OriginId = DimConstants.BeforeAdj myDbCellPkCarryoverTotal.ICId = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si, dimTypeId.Entity, FundCenter) myDbCellPkCarryoverTotal.UD5Id = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si, dimTypeId.UD5, "None") myDbCellPkCarryoverTotal.UD7Id = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si, dimTypeId.UD7, "None") myDbCellPkCarryoverTotal.UD8Id = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si, dimTypeId.UD8, "None")
Dim lTotalCarryoverAmount As List(Of DataCell) = BRApi.Finance.Data.GetDataBufferDataCells(si, myDataUnitPkCarryoverTotal, dimConstants.Periodic, myDbCellPkCarryoverTotal, True, True)
For Each amount As DataCell In lTotalAccountAmounts
Dim sEntity As String = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberName(si, dimTypeId.Entity, amount.DataCellPk.EntityId) Dim sFlow As String = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberName(si, dimTypeId.Flow, amount.DataCellPk.FlowId) Dim sUD1 As String = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberName(si, dimTypeId.UD1, amount.DataCellPk.UD1Id) Dim sUD2 As String = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberName(si, dimTypeId.UD2, amount.DataCellPk.UD2Id) Dim sUD3 As String = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberName(si, dimTypeId.UD3, amount.DataCellPk.UD3Id).Split("_")(1) Dim sUD4 As String = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberName(si, dimTypeId.UD4, amount.DataCellPk.UD4Id) Dim sUD6 As String = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberName(si, dimTypeId.UD6, amount.DataCellPk.UD6Id) Dim resultRow As DataRow = dtAll.AsEnumerable() _ .SingleOrDefault(Function(row) row.Field(Of String)("Funds Ctr") = sEntity _ AndAlso row.Field(Of String)("REQ") = sFlow) If resultRow Is Nothing Then Continue For If Not BRApi.Finance.Members.GetParents(si, BRApi.Finance.Dim.GetDimPk(si, "U1_APPN_FUND"), amount.DataCellPk.UD1Id, True, )(0).Name.XFEqualsIgnoreCase(u1) Then dtAll.Rows.Remove(resultRow) Continue For End If resultRow(Acct) = amount.CellAmount resultRow("FUND") = sUD1 resultRow("MDEP") = sUD2 resultRow("APEPT") = sUD3 resultRow("DollarType") = sUD4 resultRow("Cost Cat") = sUD6
Next 'Loop through each returned carryover amount For Each carryover As DataCell In lTotalCarryoverAmount Dim sCEntity As String = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberName(si, dimTypeId.Entity, carryover.DataCellPk.EntityId) Dim sCFlow As String = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberName(si, dimTypeId.Flow, carryover.DataCellPk.FlowId) Dim resultRow As DataRow = dtAll.AsEnumerable() _ .SingleOrDefault(Function(row) row.Field(Of String)("Funds Ctr") = sCEntity _ AndAlso row.Field(Of String)("REQ") = sCFlow) If resultRow Is Nothing Then Continue For 'if a carryover amount exists, add it to the existing Annual amount which is set on line 815 resultRow(Acct) = resultRow(Acct) + Math.Round(carryover.CellAmount,0) Next Next Next
'Process the fetched data into a format usable for report Dim sFileHeader As String = "" sFileHeader = $"SCENARIO,Funds Ctr,REQ,FUND,MDEP,APEPT,DollarType,Cost Cat,Title,Status,Total Commitment,Total Obligation,Total Commitment UFR,Total Obligation UFR,REQID,Description,Attachment,RelatedRequest,Justification,ImpactIfNotFunded,RiskIfNotFunded,CostMethodology,CostGrowthJustification,MustFund,RequestedFundSource,ArmyInitiativeDirective,CommandInitiativeDirective,ActivityExercise,ITCyberRequirement,UIC,FlexField1,FlexField2,FlexField3,FlexField4,FlexField5,EmergingRequirement,CPACandidate,PBRSubmission,UPLSubmission,ContractNumber,TaskOrderNumber,AwardTargetDate,POPExpirationDate,CME,COREmail,POCEmail,Directorate,Division,Branch,ReviewingPOCEmail,MDEPFunctionalEmail,NotificationEmailList,Comments,CreatorName,CreationDateTime,LastUpdatedName,LastUpdatedDate,StatusHistory"
' ID,AttachmentsInd, ' RelatedRequest,Description,RecurringJustification,CostMethodologyCmt,RequestedFundSource,ITCyberRqmtInd,UICAcct,FlexField1,FlexField2,FlexField3,FlexField4,FlexField5,NewRqmtInd,CPAInd,ContractNumber, ' Task Order Number,TargetDateOfAward,POPExpirationDate,FTECME,Directorate,Division,Branch,NotificationEmailList,CreatorName,CreationDateTime,LastUpdatedName,LastUpdatedDate,StatusHistory" 'Generate & write File and update FvParam for filepath needed for file viewer Return Me.GenerateReportFile(si, dtAll, sFileHeader, sCube, sBUDTime, sTemplate, sFvParam) ' Return dtAll
Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function #End Region
End Class

Imports System Imports System.Collections.Generic Imports System.Data Imports System.Data.Common Imports System.Globalization Imports System.IO Imports System.Linq Imports Microsoft.VisualBasic Imports OneStream.Finance.Database Imports OneStream.Finance.Engine Imports OneStream.Shared.Common Imports OneStream.Shared.Database Imports OneStream.Shared.Engine Imports OneStream.Shared.Wcf Imports OneStream.Stage.Database Imports OneStream.Stage.Engine Imports OneStreamWorkspacesApi Imports OneStreamWorkspacesApi.V800
'BUD_MAIN_CALC Namespace OneStream.BusinessRule.Finance.CMD_SPLN_Main_Calc Public Class MainClass
Public Function Main(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As Object Try
Select Case api.FunctionType Case Is = FinanceFunctionType.CustomCalculate
#Region "BUD_Import_Load_Cube" If args.CustomCalculateArgs.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("BUD_Import_Load_Cube") Then Me.BUD_Import_Load_Cube(si,globals,api,args) Return Nothing End If #End Region
#Region "CalculateWeightedScoreAndRank" If args.CustomCalculateArgs.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("CalculateWeightedScoreAndRank") Then Me.CalculateWeightedScoreAndRank(si, globals,api,args) Return Nothing End If #End Region
#Region "CopyAmount" If args.CustomCalculateArgs.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("CopyAmount") Then Me.CopyAmount(si,globals,api,args) Return Nothing End If #End Region
#Region "CopyApprovedAmtADM" If args.CustomCalculateArgs.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("CopyApprovedAmtADM") Then Dim calScript As String = args.CustomCalculateArgs.NameValuePairs("calScript") 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"args calScript = " & calScript) api.Data.Calculate(calScript,True) Return Nothing End If #End Region
#Region "CopyTargetManpower" If args.CustomCalculateArgs.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("CopyTargetManpower") Then Me.CopyTargetManpower(si,globals,api,args) Return Nothing End If #End Region
#Region "CopyTargetManpowerRounding" If args.CustomCalculateArgs.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("CopyTargetManpowerRounding") Then Me.CopyTargetManpowerRounding(si,globals,api,args) Return Nothing End If #End Region
#Region "CopyTGTWithholdToBUD: Copy Distribution Target/Withholds to final scenario" If args.CustomCalculateArgs.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("CopyTGTWithholdToBUD") Then Me.CopyTGTWithholdToBUD(si,globals,api,args) Return Nothing End If #End Region
#Region "FormulateREQSpread" If args.CustomCalculateArgs.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("FormulateREQSpread") Then Me.FormulateREQSpread(si,globals,api,args) Return Nothing End If #End Region
#Region "FormulateREQSpreadRounding" If args.CustomCalculateArgs.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("FormulateREQSpreadRounding") Then Me.FormulateREQSpreadRounding(si,globals,api,args) Return Nothing End If #End Region
#Region "MANPOWER_BUD_Import_Load_Cube" If args.CustomCalculateArgs.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("MANPOWER_BUD_Import_Load_Cube") Then Me.MANPOWER_BUD_Import_Load_Cube(si,globals,api,args) Return Nothing End If #End Region
#Region "ReapplyInflation" If args.CustomCalculateArgs.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("ReapplyInflation") Then Me.ReapplyInflation(si,globals,api,args) Return Nothing End If #End Region
#Region "ReturnPackage" If args.CustomCalculateArgs.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("ReturnPackage") Then Return Me.ReturnPackage(si, globals, api, args) End If #End Region
#Region "RollFwdReq: Roll Forward Requirements" If args.CustomCalculateArgs.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("RollFwdReq") Then Me.RollFwdReq(si,globals,api,args) Return Nothing End If #End Region
#Region "RollFwdReqSpread: Spread requirements across appropriations on rollover" If args.CustomCalculateArgs.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("RollFwdReqSpread") Then Me.RollFwdReqSpread(si,globals,api,args) Return Nothing End If #End Region
#Region "RollFwdReqSpreadRounding: Handle rounding to |WFYear|M12 for requirements spreading" If args.CustomCalculateArgs.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("RollFwdReqSpreadRounding") Then Me.RollFwdReqSpreadRounding(si,globals,api,args) Return Nothing End If #End Region
#Region "VerifyAndSubmit" If args.CustomCalculateArgs.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("VerifyAndSubmit") Then Return Me.VerifyAndSubmit(si, globals, api, args) End If #End Region
#Region "CopyBudtoSpendPlan" If args.CustomCalculateArgs.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("CopyBudtoSpendPlan") Then
Me.CopyBudtoSpendPlan(si,globals,api,args)
End If #End Region
Case Is = FinanceFunctionType.ReadSourceDataRecords 'Dim drCollection As New DataRecordCollection()
'Read all dataRecords from another scenario. Dim BudScores As List(Of BUD_Score) = New List(Of BUD_Score) ' For Each BUD As String In BudList Dim dt As DataTable = BRApi.Utilities.GetSessionDataTable(si,si.UserName,"BudListCVResult") BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "BudList = " & dt.Rows.Count) 'Loops For Each row As DataRow In dt.Rows Dim cleanBud_Entity = row("EntityFlow").Split(":")(0).Replace("e#[","").Replace("]","") Dim cleanBud_Id = row("EntityFlow").Split(":")(1).Replace("f#[","").Replace("]","") ' Dim cleanBud_Id As String = BUD.Substring(BUD.IndexOf("f#[") + 3, 6) Dim BudInfo As BUD_Score = New BUD_Score BudInfo.BUD_Id = cleanBud_Id ' Dim cleanBud_Entity As String = BUD.Split(":"c)(0).Split("["c)(1).Trim("]"c) BudInfo.BUD_Entity = cleanBud_Entity BudInfo.scores = New Dictionary(Of String, Decimal)
For Each kp As KeyValuePair(Of String, Decimal) In priCatNameAndWeight 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, wfProfileName) 'replace key for EEEE, UUUU and FFFF and get score. Also get the weight from the key and calculate the total Weighted score Dim priCatScore As Decimal = BRApi.Finance.Data.GetDataCellUsingMemberScript(si, WFCube, catScoreMemScript.Replace("EEEE",cleanBud_Entity ).Replace("UUUU",kp.Key).Replace("FFFF",cleanBud_Id)).DataCellEx.DataCell.CellAmount 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "pricatScore = " & pricatScore) If (priCatScore > 0) Then BudInfo.scores.Add(kp.Key, priCatScore) BudInfo.totalWeightedScore += priCatScore * (kp.Value/100) End If Next
'Add the BUD class to the list BudScores.Add(BudInfo) Next 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Here") 'Sort the reqs BudScores = BudScores.OrderByDescending(Function(u) u.totalWeightedScore).ToList
'Update the BUD with the calculated weight
Dim rank As Integer = 0 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "sFundcenter = " & sFundCenter) For Each BudScore As BUD_Score In BudScores Dim SaveTotalScoreMemScript As String = "Cb#" & WFCube & ":E#" & BudScore.BUD_Entity & ":C#Local:S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" & BudTime & ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Priority_Score:F#FFFF:O#BeforeAdj:I#" &sFundCenter & ":U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim SaveRankMemScript As String = "Cb#" & WFCube & ":E#" & BudScore.BUD_Entity & ":C#Local:S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" & BudTime & ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Priority_Calc_Rank:F#FFFF:O#BeforeAdj:I#" &sFundCenter & ":U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim SaveOverrideMemScript As String = "Cb#" & WFCube & ":E#" & BudScore.BUD_Entity & ":C#Local:S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" & BudTime & ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Priority_Override_Rank:F#FFFF:O#BeforeAdj:I#" &sFundCenter & ":U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim SaveInternalRankMemScript As String = "Cb#" & WFCube & ":E#" & BudScore.BUD_Entity & ":C#Local:S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" & BudTime & ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Internal_Rank:F#FFFF:O#BeforeAdj:I#" &sFundCenter & ":U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None"
'Update BUD Status to Prioritize Dim BudStatusMemberScript As String = "Cb#" & WFCube & ":E#" & BudScore.BUD_Entity & ":C#Local:S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" & BudTime & ":V#Annotation:A#REQ_Rqmt_Status:F#" & BudScore.BUD_Id.ToUpper() & ":O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim BudStatus As String = BRApi.Finance.Data.GetDataCellUsingMemberScript(si, WFCube, BudStatusMemberScript).DataCellEx.DataCellAnnotation Dim CurrentLevel As String = BudStatus.Substring(0,2) Dim NewStatus As String = CurrentLevel & " Prioritized"
Dim objListofScriptsWFStatus As New List(Of MemberScriptandValue) Dim objScriptValWFStatus As New MemberScriptAndValue objScriptValWFStatus.CubeName = WFCube objScriptValWFStatus.Script = BudStatusMemberScript objScriptValWFStatus.TextValue = NewStatus objScriptValWFStatus.IsNoData = False objListofScriptsWFStatus.Add(objScriptValWFStatus)
BRApi.Finance.Data.SetDataCellsUsingMemberScript(si, objListofScriptsWFStatus)
rank = rank + 1
Dim objListofScriptsTotalScore As New List(Of MemberScriptandValue) Dim objScriptValTotalScore As New MemberScriptAndValue objScriptValTotalScore.CubeName = WFCube objScriptValTotalScore.Script = SaveTotalScoreMemScript.Replace("FFFF", BudScore.BUD_Id.ToUpper()) objScriptValTotalScore.Amount = BudScore.totalWeightedScore objScriptValTotalScore.IsNoData = False objListofScriptsTotalScore.Add(objScriptValTotalScore)
BRApi.Finance.Data.SetDataCellsUsingMemberScript(si, objListofScriptsTotalScore)
Dim objListofScriptsRank As New List(Of MemberScriptandValue) Dim objScriptValRank As New MemberScriptAndValue objScriptValRank.CubeName = WFCube objScriptValRank.Script = SaveRankMemScript.Replace("FFFF", BudScore.BUD_Id.ToUpper()) objScriptValRank.Amount = rank objScriptValRank.IsNoData = False objListofScriptsRank.Add(objScriptValRank)
BRApi.Finance.Data.SetDataCellsUsingMemberScript(si, objListofScriptsRank)
Dim objListofScriptsOverride As New List(Of MemberScriptandValue) Dim objScriptValOverride As New MemberScriptAndValue objScriptValOverride.CubeName = WFCube objScriptValOverride.Script = SaveOverrideMemScript.Replace("FFFF", BudScore.BUD_Id.ToUpper()) objScriptValOverride.Amount = rank objScriptValOverride.IsNoData = False objListofScriptsOverride.Add(objScriptValOverride)
BRApi.Finance.Data.SetDataCellsUsingMemberScript(si, objListofScriptsOverride)
If sInternalRank.XFContainsIgnoreCase("True") Then
Dim objListofScriptsInternal As New List(Of MemberScriptandValue) Dim objScriptValInternal As New MemberScriptAndValue objScriptValInternal.CubeName = WFCube objScriptValInternal.Script = SaveInternalRankMemScript.Replace("FFFF", BudScore.BUD_Id.ToUpper()) objScriptValInternal.Amount = rank objScriptValInternal.IsNoData = False objListofScriptsInternal.Add(objScriptValInternal)
BRApi.Finance.Data.SetDataCellsUsingMemberScript(si, objListofScriptsInternal) End If 'set last updated name and date, and update status history Dim BR_BUD_SolutionHelper As New OneStream.BusinessRule.DashboardExtender.BUD_SolutionHelper.MainClass Dim deArgs As New DashboardExtenderArgs deArgs.FunctionType = DashboardExtenderFunctionType.ComponentSelectionChanged deArgs.FunctionName = "LastUpdated" deArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("updatedBudEntity", BudScore.BUD_Entity) deArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("updatedBudFlow", BudScore.BUD_Id.ToUpper()) BR_BUD_SolutionHelper.Main(si, globals, api, deArgs)
deArgs.FunctionType = DashboardExtenderFunctionType.ComponentSelectionChanged deArgs.FunctionName = "UpdateStatusHistory" deArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("ufrEntity", BudScore.BUD_Entity) deArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("ufrFlow", BudScore.BUD_Id.ToUpper()) deArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("FundCenter", sFundCenter) deArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("status", NewStatus) BR_BUD_SolutionHelper.Main(si, globals, api, deArgs)
Next
Return Nothing Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function
'Created 10/15/2023 - YH 'This rule gets the catogery And weight that are configured for a given fund center 'Update EH 090324 RMW-1565 Changed BudTime to annual for centralized text update Private Function GetCategoryAndWeight(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As Object Try 'Get the list of catagories Dim WFCube = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim WFScenario As String = ScenarioDimHelper.GetNameFromId(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey) Dim WFYear As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetYearFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) Dim BudTime As String = WFYear & "M12"
Dim sFundCenter As String = args.CustomCalculateArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("FundCenter") 'Brapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"entity = " & BudEntity) Dim priCatMembers As List(Of MemberInfo) Dim priFilter As String = "U5#UFR_Priority_Category.Children" Dim priCatDimPk As DimPk = BRApi.Finance.Dim.GetDimPk(si, "U5_Main") priCatMembers = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMembersUsingFilter(si, priCatDimPk, priFilter, True)
Dim catNameMemScript As String = "Cb#" & WFCube & ":E#" & sFundCenter & ":C#Local:S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" & BudTime & ":V#Annotation:A#REQ_Priority_Cat_Name:F#None:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#UUUU:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim catWeightMemScript As String = "Cb#" & WFCube & ":E#" & sFundCenter & ":C#Local:S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" & BudTime & ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Priority_Cat_Weight:F#None:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#UUUU:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None"
Dim priCatName As String = "" Dim priCatWeight As Decimal
Dim priCatNameAndWeight As Dictionary(Of String, Decimal) = New Dictionary(Of String, Decimal) For Each pricat As MemberInfo In priCatMembers priCatName = BRApi.Finance.Data.GetDataCellUsingMemberScript(si, WFCube, catNameMemScript.Replace("UUUU",priCat.Member.Name)).DataCellEx.DataCellAnnotation 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "priCatName = " & priCatName) If (Not String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(priCatName)) Then priCatWeight = BRApi.Finance.Data.GetDataCellUsingMemberScript(si, WFCube, catWeightMemScript.Replace("UUUU",priCat.Member.Name)).DataCellEx.DataCell.CellAmount 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "priCatWeight = " & priCatWeight) priCatNameAndWeight.Add(priCat.Member.Name, priCatWeight) End If Next
Return priCatNameAndWeight
Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function

#Region "CopyAmount" Public Function CopyAmount(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As Object Try

Dim srcScript As String = "E#" & srcEntity & ":S#" & srcSenario & ":T#" & FY & ":F#" & srcFlow & ":I#" & srcEntity trgtScript = "E#" & trgtEntity & ":S#" & trgtScenario & ":T#" & FY & ":F#" & trgtFlow & ":I#" & trgtEntity

api.Data.ClearCalculatedData(trgtScript & Phased_Oblig, True, True, True, True) api.Data.ClearCalculatedData(trgtScript & Phased_Comit, True, True, True, True) api.Data.ClearCalculatedData(trgtScript & UFR_Oblig, True, True, True, True) api.Data.ClearCalculatedData(trgtScript & UFR_Comit, True, True, True, True)
api.Data.Calculate(calScript_PhasedOblig,True) api.Data.Calculate(calScript_Phasedcomit,True) api.Data.Calculate(calScript_UFROblig,True) api.Data.Calculate(calScript_UFRComit,True)

Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function #End Region
#Region "CopyTargetManpower" 'Updated 12/03/2024 by Fronz - changed BO5 to BOC & added the 'Clear Existing Data' lines of code Public Function CopyTargetManpower(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As Object Try Dim sFlow As String = args.CustomCalculateArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("Flow") Dim sEntity As String = args.CustomCalculateArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("Entity").Replace("E#","") Dim objDimPk As New DimPk Dim sAPPN As String = sFlow.Replace("REQ_00_CP_","") Dim APPNParent As String = "" Dim ParentmembList As List(Of memberinfo) = New List(Of MemberInfo) Dim bAPPNMatch As Boolean Dim sTargetYearMonth As String = api.Pov.Time.Name Dim sTargetYear As String = sTargetYearMonth.Substring(0,4) Dim sSourcePosition As String = "Initial_Distribution_FY" & sTargetYear Dim sCube As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim sTargetScenario As String = api.Pov.Scenario.Name Dim sSrcMbrScript As String = "" Dim sPayCostSourceMbrScript As String = "Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sSourcePosition & ":T#" & sTargetYear & ":C#Local:E#" & sEntity & ":V#Periodic:A#Pay:O#BeforeAdj:U7#Top:U8#Top:I#Top:F#Baseline:U1#Top:U2#Top:U3#Top:U4#Top:U5#Top:U6#Top" Dim PayCostSourceCell As String = api.Data.GetDataCellEx(sPayCostSourceMbrScript).DataCell.CellAmount 'check if data exists If PayCostSourceCell.XFEqualsIgnoreCase(0) Then Throw New System.Exception(vbCrLf & vbCrLf & "Import CivPay: Source data does not exist for this Funds Center") End If
If Not PayCostSourceCell.XFEqualsIgnoreCase(0) And Not sTargetYearMonth.XFContainsIgnoreCase("M12") Then
sSrcMbrScript = "RemoveZeros(Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sSourcePosition & ":T#" & sTargetYear & "M12:C#Local:E#" & sEntity sSrcMbrScript &= ":V#Periodic:A#Pay:F#Baseline:O#BeforeAdj:I#Top:U7#Top:U8#Top)"
Dim dbFundingLines As DataBuffer = Nothing Try dbFundingLines = api.Data.GetDataBufferUsingFormula(sSrcMbrScript,,False) Catch ex As Exception Throw New System.Exception( "Import Manpower: Invalid Source Member Script. sSrcMbrScript=" & sSrcMbrScript) End Try 'brapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"sSrcMbrScript = " &sSrcMbrScript) For Each dcCell As DataBufferCell In dbFundingLines.DataBufferCells.values Dim sU1 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD1Name(api) Dim sU2 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD2Name(api) Dim sU3 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD3Name(api) Dim sU4 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD4Name(api) Dim sU5 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD5Name(api) Dim sU6 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD6Name(api) 'brapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"sU1 = " &sU1) bAPPNMatch = True objDimPk = BRApi.Finance.Dim.GetDimPk(si, "U1_APPN_FUND") ParentmembList = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMembersUsingFilter(si, objDimPk, "U1#" & sU1 & ".Parents", True) 'brapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"ParentmembListCount = " & ParentmembList.Count) For Each Parent In ParentmembList
If Not sAPPN.XFEqualsIgnoreCase(Parent.Member.Name) Then bAPPNMatch = False End If Next If Not bAPPNMatch Then Continue For
Dim dAmt As Decimal = dcCell.CellAmount Dim dFinalAmount As Decimal Dim sAnnualCompHoursSourceMbrScript As String = "Cb#ARMY:S#" & sSourcePosition & ":T#" & sTargetYear & "M12:C#Local:E#Army_General:V#Periodic:A#Compensable_Hrs:O#BeforeAdj:U7#None:U8#None:I#None:F#None:U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None" Dim AnnualCompHoursourceCell As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCellEx(sAnnualCompHoursSourceMbrScript).DataCell.CellAmount 'brapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"inside if pay cost inside for loop") Dim hourlyAmount As Decimal = dAmt/AnnualCompHoursourceCell Dim sCompHoursAcct As String = "" Select Case sTargetYearMonth.ToUpper Case sTargetYear & "M1" sCompHoursAcct = "Compensable_Hrs_M1" Case sTargetYear & "M2" sCompHoursAcct = "Compensable_Hrs_M2" Case sTargetYear & "M3" sCompHoursAcct = "Compensable_Hrs_M3" Case sTargetYear & "M4" sCompHoursAcct = "Compensable_Hrs_M4" Case sTargetYear & "M5" sCompHoursAcct = "Compensable_Hrs_M5" Case sTargetYear & "M6" sCompHoursAcct = "Compensable_Hrs_M6" Case sTargetYear & "M7" sCompHoursAcct = "Compensable_Hrs_M7" Case sTargetYear & "M8" sCompHoursAcct = "Compensable_Hrs_M8" Case sTargetYear & "M9" sCompHoursAcct = "Compensable_Hrs_M9" Case sTargetYear & "M10" sCompHoursAcct = "Compensable_Hrs_M10" Case sTargetYear & "M11" sCompHoursAcct = "Compensable_Hrs_M11" End Select Dim sMonthlyCompHoursSourceMbrScript As String = "Cb#ARMY:S#" & sSourcePosition & ":T#" & sTargetYear & "M12:C#Local:E#Army_General:V#Periodic:A#" & sCompHoursAcct & ":O#BeforeAdj:U7#None:U8#None:I#None:F#None:U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None" Dim MonthlyCompHoursourceCell As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCellEx(sMonthlyCompHoursSourceMbrScript).DataCell.CellAmount
dFinalAmount = math.Round(MonthlyCompHoursourceCell*hourlyAmount,0)
'brapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"dFinalAmount = " & sTargetYearMonth & ": " & dFinalAmount & ": rounded=" & dFinalAmount)
Dim sTgtMbrScriptFormObl As String = "Cb#" & sCube & ":E#" & sEntity & ":C#Local:S#" & sTargetScenario & ":T#" & sTargetYearMonth & ":V#Periodic:A#Phased_Obligation_Base:F#" & sFlow & ":O#Forms:I#" & sEntity & ":U1#" & sU1 & ":U2#" & sU2 & ":U3#" & sU3 & ":U4#" & sU4 & ":U5#" & sU5 & ":U6#GFEBS_01_General:U7#None:U8#None" Dim sTgtMbrScriptFormCom As String = "Cb#" & sCube & ":E#" & sEntity & ":C#Local:S#" & sTargetScenario & ":T#" & sTargetYearMonth & ":V#Periodic:A#Phased_Commitment:F#" & sFlow & ":O#Forms:I#" & sEntity & ":U1#" & sU1 & ":U2#" & sU2 & ":U3#" & sU3 & ":U4#" & sU4 & ":U5#" & sU5 & ":U6#GFEBS_01_General:U7#None:U8#None"
Dim targetCell As DataCell Dim targetCellInfo As DataCellInfoUsingMemberScript
'Obliation set cell targetCellInfo = BRApi.Finance.Data.GetDataCellUsingMemberScript(si, sCube, sTgtMbrScriptFormObl) targetCell = targetCellInfo.DataCellEx.DataCell
api.Data.SetDataCell(api.Data.GetDataCell(targetCell.DataCellPk).DataCellPk.CreateMemberScriptBuilder(api).GetMemberScript, dFinalAmount, False, True)
'commitment set cell targetCellInfo = BRApi.Finance.Data.GetDataCellUsingMemberScript(si, sCube, sTgtMbrScriptFormCom) targetCell = targetCellInfo.DataCellEx.DataCell
api.Data.SetDataCell(api.Data.GetDataCell(targetCell.DataCellPk).DataCellPk.CreateMemberScriptBuilder(api).GetMemberScript, dFinalAmount, False, True) Next End If If sTargetYearMonth.XFEqualsIgnoreCase(sTargetYear & "M12") sSrcMbrScript = "RemoveZeros(Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sSourcePosition & ":T#" & sTargetYear & "M12:C#Local:E#" & sEntity sSrcMbrScript &= ":V#Periodic:A#Total_Auth_Adj_Mpwr:F#Baseline:O#BeforeAdj:I#Top:U7#Top:U8#Top)"
Dim dbFundingLines As DataBuffer = Nothing Try dbFundingLines = api.Data.GetDataBufferUsingFormula(sSrcMbrScript,,False)
Catch ex As Exception Throw New System.Exception( "Import Manpower: Invalid Source Member Script. sSrcMbrScript=" & sSrcMbrScript) End Try For Each dcCell As DataBufferCell In dbFundingLines.DataBufferCells.values Dim sU1 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD1Name(api) Dim sU2 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD2Name(api) Dim sU3 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD3Name(api) Dim sU4 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD4Name(api) Dim sU5 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD5Name(api) Dim sU6 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD6Name(api)
bAPPNMatch = True objDimPk = BRApi.Finance.Dim.GetDimPk(si, "U1_APPN_FUND") ParentmembList = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMembersUsingFilter(si, objDimPk, "U1#" & sU1 & ".Parents", True) For Each Parent In ParentmembList If Not sAPPN.XFEqualsIgnoreCase(Parent.Member.Name) Then bAPPNMatch = False End If Next If Not bAPPNMatch Then Continue For
Dim sREQ_DCOSourceMbrScript As String = "Cb#ARMY:S#" & sSourcePosition & ":T#" & sTargetYear & "M12:C#Local:E#" & sEntity & ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_DCO:O#BeforeAdj:U7#Top:U8#Top:I#Top:F#Baseline:U1#" & sU1 & ":U2#" & sU2 & ":U3#" & sU3 & ":U4#" & sU4 & ":U5#" & sU5 & ":U6#" & sU6 Dim REQ_DCOsourceCell As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCellEx(sREQ_DCOSourceMbrScript).DataCell.CellAmount
Dim dAmt As Decimal = dcCell.CellAmount + REQ_DCOsourceCell
Dim sTgtMbrScriptForm As String = "Cb#" & sCube & ":E#" & sEntity & ":C#Local:S#" & sTargetScenario & ":T#" & sTargetYear & "M12:V#Periodic:A#Auth_Mpwr:F#" & sFlow & ":O#Forms:I#" & sEntity & ":U1#" & sU1 & ":U2#" & sU2 & ":U3#" & sU3 & ":U4#" & sU4 & ":U5#" & sU5 & ":U6#" & sU6 & ":U7#None:U8#None" 'brapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"dAmtFTE = " & sTgtMbrScriptForm & ": " & math.Round(dAmt,0)) Dim targetCell As DataCell Dim targetCellInfo As DataCellInfoUsingMemberScript targetCellInfo = BRApi.Finance.Data.GetDataCellUsingMemberScript(si, sCube, sTgtMbrScriptForm) targetCell = targetCellInfo.DataCellEx.DataCell
api.Data.SetDataCell(api.Data.GetDataCell(targetCell.DataCellPk).DataCellPk.CreateMemberScriptBuilder(api).GetMemberScript, math.Round(dAmt,0), False, True) Next End If

api.Data.SetDataCell(api.Data.GetDataCell(targetCell.DataCellPk).DataCellPk.CreateMemberScriptBuilder(api).GetMemberScript, dFinalAmount, False, True)

api.Data.SetDataCell(api.Data.GetDataCell(targetCell.DataCellPk).DataCellPk.CreateMemberScriptBuilder(api).GetMemberScript, dFinalAmount, False, True) Next

#Region "FormulateREQSpread" Public Function FormulateREQSpread(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As Object Try Dim wfProfileName As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).Name Dim WFCube = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim WFScenario As String = ScenarioDimHelper.GetNameFromId(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey) Dim WFYear As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetYearFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey)
Dim sCurrScenario As String = api.Pov.Scenario.Name Dim sCurrTime As String = api.Pov.Time.Name Dim sPOVEntity As String = api.Pov.Entity.Name Dim sFlow As String = api.Pov.Flow.Name Dim sIC As String = api.Pov.IC.Name Dim sU1 As String = api.Pov.UD1.Name Dim sU2 As String = api.Pov.UD2.Name Dim sU3 As String = api.Pov.UD3.Name Dim sU4 As String = api.Pov.UD4.Name Dim sU6 As String = api.Pov.UD6.Name 'Brapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "sCurrScenario " & sCurrScenario & "sCurrTime " & sCurrTime & "sPOVEntity " & sPOVEntity & "sFlow" & sFlow & "sIC" & sIC & "sU1" & sU1 & "sU2" & sU2 & "sU3" & sU3 & "sU6" & sU6)
Dim SourceIntersectionOblig As String = "Cb#" & WFCube & ":E#" & sPOVEntity & ":C#Local:S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" & WFYear & "M12" & ":V#Periodic:A#Phased_Obligation_Base:F#" & sFlow & ":O#BeforeAdj:I#" & sIC & ":U1#" & sU1 & ":U2#" & sU2 & ":U3#" & sU3 & ":U4#" & sU4 & ":U5#None:U6#" & sU6 & ":U7#None:U8#None" Dim SourceAmtOblig As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCell(SourceIntersectionOblig).CellAmount 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Source total: " & SourceAmtOblig.ToString)
'====== GET APPN_FUND AND PARENT APPN_L2 ======
Dim U1Name As String = sU1 Dim U1DimPk As DimPk = BRApi.Finance.Dim.GetDimPk(si, "U1_APPN_FUND") Dim U1MemberID As Integer = api.Members.GetMemberId(dimType.UD1.Id, U1Name) Dim U1ParentName As String = api.Members.GetParents(U1DimPk, U1MemberId, False, )(0).Name + "_General" 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, U1Name + " " + U1ParentName & " REQ=" & Req)
'====== GET TOTAL PERCENT OBLIG ======
Dim OBL_SpreadYearTotal As String = "Cb#" + WFCube + ":E#" + WFCube + "_General:C#Local:S#" + WFScenario + ":T#" + WFYear.ToString + ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Phased_Obligation_Spread_Prct:F#None:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#" + U1ParentName + ":U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim OBL_SpreadYearTotalPct As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCell(OBL_SpreadYearTotal).CellAmount
Dim OBL_SpreadYearNextM12 As String = "Cb#" + WFCube + ":E#" + WFCube + "_General:C#Local:S#" + WFScenario + ":T#" + (WFYear+1).ToString + "M12:V#Periodic:A#REQ_Phased_Obligation_Spread_Prct:F#None:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#" + U1ParentName + ":U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim OBL_SpreadYearNextM12Pct As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCell(OBL_SpreadYearNextM12).CellAmount
Dim OBL_PercentTotal As Decimal = OBL_SpreadYearTotalPct + OBL_SpreadYearNextM12Pct 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "% Total: " & OBL_PercentTotal.ToString)
'====== GET MONTHLY PERCENT ======
Dim OBL_SpreadYearMonth As String = "Cb#" + WFCube + ":E#" + WFCube + "_General:C#Local:S#" + WFScenario + ":T#" + sCurrTime + ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Phased_Obligation_Spread_Prct:F#None:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#" + U1ParentName + ":U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim OBL_SpreadYearMonthPct As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCell(OBL_SpreadYearMonth).CellAmount/100 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "OBL_SpreadYearMonth: " & OBL_SpreadYearMonthPct.ToString)
'====== GET TARGET INTERSECTION ======
Dim OBL_TargetIntersection As String ="" Dim OBL_TargetAmt As Decimal
OBL_TargetIntersection = "Cb#" & WFCube & ":E#" & sPOVEntity & ":C#Local:S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" & sCurrTime OBL_TargetIntersection &= ":V#Periodic:A#Phased_Obligation_Base:F#" & sFlow & ":O#Forms:I#" & sIC & ":U1#" & sU1 & ":U2#" & sU2 & ":U3#" & sU3 & ":U4#" & sU4 & ":U5#None:U6#" & sU6 & ":U7#None:U8#None" Dim targetCelloblig As DataCell Dim targetCellInfooblig As DataCellInfoUsingMemberScript targetCellInfooblig = BRApi.Finance.Data.GetDataCellUsingMemberScript(si, wfCube, OBL_TargetIntersection) targetCelloblig = targetCellInfooblig.DataCellEx.DataCell
If OBL_PercentTotal = 100 Then OBL_TargetAmt = math.Round(SourceAmtOblig * OBL_SpreadYearMonthPct)
api.Data.SetDataCell(api.Data.GetDataCell(targetCelloblig.DataCellPk).DataCellPk.CreateMemberScriptBuilder(api).GetMemberScript, OBL_TargetAmt, False, True)
Else If (OBL_PercentTotal = 0 Or OBL_PercentTotal < 100) And sCurrTime.XFContainsIgnoreCase(WFYear) Then
OBL_TargetAmt = Math.Round(SourceAmtOblig/12) api.Data.SetDataCell(api.Data.GetDataCell(targetCelloblig.DataCellPk).DataCellPk.CreateMemberScriptBuilder(api).GetMemberScript, OBL_TargetAmt, False, True)
Else OBL_TargetAmt = 0
End If
'=====Commitment Source ========
Dim SourceIntersectionCommit As String = "Cb#" & WFCube & ":E#" & sPOVEntity & ":C#Local:S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" & WFYear & "M12" & ":V#Periodic:A#Phased_Commitment:F#" & sFlow & ":O#BeforeAdj:I#" & sIC & ":U1#" & sU1 & ":U2#" & sU2 & ":U3#" & sU3 & ":U4#" & sU4 & ":U5#None:U6#" & sU6 & ":U7#None:U8#None" Dim SourceAmtCommit As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCell(SourceIntersectionCommit).CellAmount
'====== GET TOTAL PERCENT Comit ======
Dim Comit_SpreadYearTotal As String = "Cb#" + WFCube + ":E#" + WFCube + "_General:C#Local:S#" + WFScenario + ":T#" + WFYear.ToString + ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Phased_Commitment_Spread_Prct:F#None:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#" + U1ParentName + ":U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim Comit_SpreadYearTotalPct As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCell(Comit_SpreadYearTotal).CellAmount
Dim Comit_SpreadYearNextM12 As String = "Cb#" + WFCube + ":E#" + WFCube + "_General:C#Local:S#" + WFScenario + ":T#" + (WFYear+1).ToString + "M12:V#Periodic:A#REQ_Phased_Commitment_Spread_Prct:F#None:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#" + U1ParentName + ":U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim Comit_SpreadYearNextM12Pct As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCell(Comit_SpreadYearNextM12).CellAmount
Dim Comit_PercentTotal As Decimal = Comit_SpreadYearTotalPct + Comit_SpreadYearNextM12Pct 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "comit spread " & Comit_SpreadYearNextM12)
'====== GET MONTHLY PERCENT ======
Dim Comit_SpreadYearMonth As String = "Cb#" + WFCube + ":E#" + WFCube + "_General:C#Local:S#" + WFScenario + ":T#" + sCurrTime + ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Phased_Commitment_Spread_Prct:F#None:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#" + U1ParentName + ":U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim Comit_SpreadYearMonthPct As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCell(Comit_SpreadYearMonth).CellAmount/100 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Comit_SpreadYearMonth: " & Comit_SpreadYearMonthPct.ToString & "Currtime" & sCurrTime)
'====== GET TARGET INTERSECTION =====
Dim Comit_TargetIntersection As String ="" Dim Comit_TargetAmt As Decimal
Comit_TargetIntersection = "Cb#" & WFCube & ":E#" & sPOVEntity & ":C#Local:S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" & sCurrTime Comit_TargetIntersection &= ":V#Periodic:A#Phased_Commitment:F#" & sFlow & ":O#Forms:I#" & sIC & ":U1#" & sU1 & ":U2#" & sU2 & ":U3#" & sU3 & ":U4#" & sU4 & ":U5#None:U6#" & sU6 & ":U7#None:U8#None"

sKey As String = "S#" & sRow_Scenario & ":T#" & sRow_FiscalYear & "M12:E#" & sRow_Fundcenter & ":U1#" & sRow_FundCode & ":U2#" & sRow_MDEP & ":U3#" & sRow_APE_PT & ":U4#" & sRow_DT & ":U5#" & #Region "ReapplyInflation" Public Function ReapplyInflation(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As Object Try
'========== routine vars ============================================================================================================ Dim wfProfileName As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).Name Dim wfCube As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim wfScenarioName As String = ScenarioDimHelper.GetNameFromId(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey) Dim iCurrScenarioYear As Integer = Strings.Right(wfScenarioName,4).XFConvertToInt Dim scbxEntity As String= args.CustomCalculateArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("Entity") Dim sFinalEntity As String = scbxEntity.Replace("_General","") Dim sSrcMbrScript As String = "" Dim sSrcMbrScriptFilter As String = "" Dim sTgtMbrScript As String = ""
'------------------------------------- ' Get All BUD E#F# List '------------------------------------- args.MemberListArgs = New MemberListArgs args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("EntityMbrFilter", sFinalEntity) args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("ReturnDim", "E#F#") args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("TitleSearch","") args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("Mode", "Current")
Dim lsBudAllList As List(Of String) = BUD_Member_Lists.GetAllBudListReapplyInflation(si, globals, api, args)
If lsBudAllList.Count = 0 Then Return lsBudAllList
'Reduce list to Entity equals cbx Entity Dim lsreapplylist As New List(Of String) For Each sreapplyMbrScript As String In lsBudAllList
Dim sEntity As String = sreapplyMbrScript.Split("[")(1).Split("]")(0) Dim sFlow As String = sreapplyMbrScript.Split("[")(2).Split("]")(0)
'----- only include BUD for the entity we are at ----- If Not sEntity.XFEqualsIgnoreCase(sFinalEntity) Then Continue For
'--------- Filter out reqs at L1 and L2 Status --------- sSrcMbrScriptFilter = "Cb#" & wfCube & ":S#" & wfScenarioName & ":T#" & (iCurrScenarioYear).ToString & ":C#USD:E#" & sEntity sSrcMbrScriptFilter &= ":V#Annotation:A#REQ_Rqmt_Status:F#" & sFlow & ":O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#ReadOnlyAnnotation"
Dim sFilterStatus As String = api.data.GetDataCellEx(sSrcMbrScriptFilter).DataCellAnnotation
If sFilterStatus.XFContainsIgnoreCase("L1") Or sFilterStatus.XFContainsIgnoreCase("L2") Then Continue For
If lsreapplylist.Count = 0 Then lsreapplylist.Add("E#" & sEntity & ":F#" & sFlow) Else lsreapplylist.Add(", E#" & sEntity & ":F#" & sFlow) End If
Next
'----- exit if no requirements ----- If lsreapplylist.Count = 0 Then Return lsreapplylist
'------------------------------------- ' loop thru reqs within data unit '------------------------------------- For Each sreapplyMbrScript As String In lsreapplylist Dim sEntity As String = sreapplyMbrScript.Replace("E#", "~").Split("~")(1).Split(":")(0) Dim sFlow As String = sreapplyMbrScript.Replace("F#", "~").Split("~")(1).Split(":")(0)
'------------------------------------- ' Clear pre-existing amounts '------------------------------------- 'api.Data.ClearCalculatedData("Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sCurrScenario & ":T#" & & (iCurrScenarioYear+4).ToString & ":C#USD:E#" & sEntity & ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Requested_Amt:F#" & sFlow, True, True, True, True)
'--------- copy req amounts --------- sSrcMbrScript = "RemoveZeros(Cb#" & wfCube & ":S#" & wfScenarioName & ":T#" & (iCurrScenarioYear+3).ToString & ":C#USD:E#" & sEntity sSrcMbrScript &= ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Requested_Amt:F#" & sFlow & ":O#BeforeAdj:U7#None:U8#None)"
Dim dbFundingLines As DataBuffer = Nothing Try dbFundingLines = api.Data.GetDataBufferUsingFormula(sSrcMbrScript,,False)
Catch ex As Exception Throw New System.Exception( "Reapply Inflation: Invalid Soure Requested Amount Member Script. sSrcMbrScript=" & sSrcMbrScript) End Try
For Each dcCell As DataBufferCell In dbFundingLines.DataBufferCells.values Dim sIC As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetICName(api) Dim sU1 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD1Name(api) Dim sU2 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD2Name(api) Dim sU3 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD3Name(api) Dim sU4 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD4Name(api) Dim sU5 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD5Name(api) Dim sU6 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD6Name(api)
Dim sAPPN As String = "" If sU1.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("none") Then sAPPN = "None" Else sAPPN = api.Members.GetParents(BRApi.Finance.Dim.GetDimPk(si, "U1_APPN_FUND"), api.Members.GetMemberId(dimtypeid.UD1, sU1), True )(0).Name & "_General" End If Dim sInfRateScript As String = "Cb#" & wfCube & ":S#" & wfScenarioName & ":T#" & iCurrScenarioYear.ToString & ":C#USD:E#" & wfCube & "_General:V#Periodic:A#PGM_Inflation_Rate_Amt:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:F#None" sInfRateScript &= ":U1#" & sAPPN & ":U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None"
Dim dInflationRate As Decimal = 0 Try dInflationRate =api.data.GetDataCellEx(sInfRateScript).DataCell.CellAmount
Catch ex As Exception Throw New System.Exception( "Reapply Inflation: Invalid Inflation Rate Member Script. sInfRateScript=" & sInfRateScript) End Try
Dim dAmt As Decimal = Math.Round(dcCell.CellAmount * (1 + (dInflationRate/100)))
Dim sTgtMbrScriptForm As String = "Cb#" &wfCube & ":S#" & wfScenarioName & ":T#" & (iCurrScenarioYear+4).ToString & ":C#Local:E#" & sEntity & ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Requested_Amt:O#Forms:U7#None:U8#None"& ":I#" & sIC & ":F#" & sFlow & ":U1#" & sU1 & ":U2#" & sU2 & ":U3#" & sU3 & ":U4#" & sU4 & ":U5#" & sU5 & ":U6#" & sU6
Dim targetCell As DataCell Dim targetCellInfo As DataCellInfoUsingMemberScript targetCellInfo = BRApi.Finance.Data.GetDataCellUsingMemberScript(si, wfCube, sTgtMbrScriptForm) targetCell = targetCellInfo.DataCellEx.DataCell
'Only write Labor Cost to cube if NOT manually inputted by user. If (targetCell.CellStatus.StorageType.ToString <> "Input" Or targetCell.CellStatus.IsRealData <> "True") Then api.Data.SetDataCell(api.Data.GetDataCell(targetCell.DataCellPk).DataCellPk.CreateMemberScriptBuilder(api).GetMemberScript, dAmt, False, True) End If Next Next
Return Nothing Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function #End Region
#Region "ReturnPackage" Private Function ReturnPackage(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As Object Dim return_message As String = "" Dim destination As String = args.CustomCalculateArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("destination") Dim cbxentity As String = args.CustomCalculateArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("cbxentity") Dim entity As String = args.CustomCalculateArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("entity") Dim u1 As String = args.CustomCalculateArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("u1")
' Dim entity As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("entity") ' Dim u1 As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("u1") 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Entity: " & entity & vbCrLf & _ ' "U1: " & u1)
If String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(entity) OrElse String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(u1) Then return_message = "Please select a Funds Center and Appropriation to submit a package" Throw New XFUserMsgException(si, New Exception(return_message)) End If
Dim cube As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim scenario As String = ScenarioDimHelper.GetNameFromID(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey) Dim time As String = BRApi.Finance.Time.GetNameFromId(si, BRApi.Workflow.General.GetWorkflowUnitPk(si).TimeKey) 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Cube: " & cube & vbCrLf & _ ' "Scenario: " & scenario & vbCrLf & _ ' "Time: " & time)
' Check if workflow is completed/locked If (BRApi.Workflow.General.GetUserWorkflowInitInfo(si).GetSelectedWorkflowInfo.GetOverallStatusText(False).Contains("Completed") And _ Not BRApi.Workflow.General.GetUserWorkflowInitInfo(si).GetSelectedWorkflowInfo.GetOverallStatusText(False).Contains("Load Completed")) Or _ (BRApi.Workflow.Status.GetWorkflowStatus(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk, True).Locked) return_message = "Notice: No updates are allowed. Workflow was marked ""Complete"" by Command HQ." Throw New XFUserMsgException(si, New Exception(return_message)) End If
Dim is_completed_f_cell As String = $"Cb#{cube}:E#{cbxentity}:C#Local:S#{scenario}:T#{time}M12:V#Annotation:A#REQ_Allow_Creation:F#None:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim is_completed_f As String = api.Data.GetDataCellEx(is_completed_f_cell,).DataCellAnnotation Dim is_completed_v_cell As String = $"Cb#{cube}:E#{cbxentity}:C#Local:S#{scenario}:T#{time}M12:V#Annotation:A#REQ_Allow_Validation:F#None:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim is_completed_v As String = api.Data.GetDataCellEx(is_completed_v_cell,).DataCellAnnotation If api.workflow.GetWorkflowUnitInfo.ProfileName.XFContainsIgnoreCase("formulate") And is_completed_f.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("No") Or _ api.workflow.GetWorkflowUnitInfo.ProfileName.XFContainsIgnoreCase("validate") And is_completed_v.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("No") Then return_message = "Notice: No updates are allowed. Workflow was locked by manager." Throw New XFUserMsgException(si, New Exception(return_message)) End If
args.MemberListArgs = New MemberListArgs args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("ReturnDim","E#F#") args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("cbxEntity",cbxentity) args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("EntityFilter",entity) args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("U1ParentFilter",u1) Dim requirements_list As List(Of String) = BUD_Member_Lists.GetDimMbrsList(si,globals,api,args)
Dim status As String = "REQ_Rqmt_Status" Dim base_script_status As String = ":C#Local:V#Annotation:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None"
Dim status_script As String = "" Dim req_status As String = "" Dim new_status As String = "" Dim fc_level As Integer
Dim objListofScriptsWFStatus As New List(Of MemberScriptandValue) Dim objScriptValWFStatus As New MemberScriptAndValue objScriptValWFStatus.CubeName = cube objScriptValWFStatus.IsNoData = False
Dim args2 As New DashboardExtenderArgs Dim reason As String = args.CustomCalculateArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("reason") Dim requirement_flow_list As String = ""
Dim workflow_name As String = api.workflow.GetWorkflowUnitInfo.ProfileName
' RETURN TO FORMULATE If destination.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("formulate") Then For Each requirement_script In requirements_list status_script = $"Cb#{cube}:S#{scenario}:T#{time}M12:A#{status}:" & requirement_script & base_script_status req_status = api.Data.GetDataCellEx(status_script).DataCellAnnotation new_status = req_status.Split(" ")(0) & " Returned to Formulation" 'return_message &= status_script & ": " & req_status & " > " & new_status & vbCrLf objScriptValWFStatus.Script = status_script objScriptValWFStatus.TextValue = new_status objListofScriptsWFStatus.Add(objScriptValWFStatus) BRApi.Finance.Data.SetDataCellsUsingMemberScript(si, objListofScriptsWFStatus) ' Get requirement ID list for email Dim requirement_script_flow As String = Strings.Split(Strings.Split(requirement_script, "f#[")(1), "]")(0) requirement_flow_list &= requirement_script_flow & "," Next requirement_flow_list = requirement_flow_list.Substring(0, requirement_flow_list.Length - 1)
args2.FunctionName = "SendPackageStatusChangeEmail" args2.FunctionType = DashboardExtenderFunctionType.ComponentSelectionChanged args2.NameValuePairs.Add("requirement_numbers", requirement_flow_list) args2.NameValuePairs.Add("funds_center", entity) args2.NameValuePairs.Add("appropriation", u1) args2.NameValuePairs.Add("status", new_status) args2.NameValuePairs.Add("reason", reason) BR_BUD_SolutionHelper.SendPackageStatusChangeEmail(si, globals, api, args2)
' RETURN TO VALIDATE Else If destination.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("validate") Then For Each requirement_script In requirements_list status_script = $"Cb#{cube}:S#{scenario}:T#{time}M12:A#{status}:" & requirement_script & base_script_status req_status = api.Data.GetDataCellEx(status_script).DataCellAnnotation new_status = req_status.Split(" ")(0) & " Returned to Validation" 'return_message &= status_script & ": " & req_status & " > " & new_status & vbCrLf objScriptValWFStatus.Script = status_script objScriptValWFStatus.TextValue = new_status objListofScriptsWFStatus.Add(objScriptValWFStatus) BRApi.Finance.Data.SetDataCellsUsingMemberScript(si, objListofScriptsWFStatus) ' Get requirement ID list for email Dim requirement_script_flow As String = Strings.Split(Strings.Split(requirement_script, "f#[")(1), "]")(0) requirement_flow_list &= requirement_script_flow & "," Next requirement_flow_list = requirement_flow_list.Substring(0, requirement_flow_list.Length - 1)
args2.FunctionName = "SendPackageStatusChangeEmail" args2.FunctionType = DashboardExtenderFunctionType.ComponentSelectionChanged args2.NameValuePairs.Add("requirement_numbers", requirement_flow_list) args2.NameValuePairs.Add("funds_center", entity) args2.NameValuePairs.Add("appropriation", u1) args2.NameValuePairs.Add("status", new_status) args2.NameValuePairs.Add("reason", reason) BR_BUD_SolutionHelper.SendPackageStatusChangeEmail(si, globals, api, args2)
' DEMOTE TO PREVIOUS LEVEL Else If destination.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("demote") Then If entity.XFEqualsIgnoreCase(cbxentity) Then return_message = "Cannot demote package below the level of its funds center." Throw New XFUserMsgException(si, New Exception(return_message)) End If For Each requirement_script In requirements_list status_script = $"Cb#{cube}:S#{scenario}:T#{time}M12:A#{status}:" & requirement_script & base_script_status req_status = api.Data.GetDataCellEx(status_script).DataCellAnnotation fc_level = req_status.Substring(1,1) + 1 new_status = "L" & fc_level.ToString & " Demoted from " & req_status.Split(" ")(0) 'return_message &= "Base: " & status_script & ": " & req_status & " > " & new_status & vbCrLf & entity & cbxentity & vbCrLf objScriptValWFStatus.Script = status_script objScriptValWFStatus.TextValue = new_status objListofScriptsWFStatus.Add(objScriptValWFStatus) BRApi.Finance.Data.SetDataCellsUsingMemberScript(si, objListofScriptsWFStatus) Next
' DEMOTE L2 Approved REQs Else If destination.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("demoteCert") Then If entity.XFEqualsIgnoreCase(cbxentity) Then return_message = "Cannot demote package below the level of its funds center." Throw New XFUserMsgException(si, New Exception(return_message)) End If For Each requirement_script In requirements_list status_script = $"Cb#{cube}:S#{scenario}:T#{time}M12:A#{status}:" & requirement_script & base_script_status req_status = api.Data.GetDataCellEx(status_script).DataCellAnnotation fc_level = req_status.Substring(1,1) + 1 new_status = "L2 Ready for Approval" 'return_message &= "Base: " & status_script & ": " & req_status & " > " & new_status & vbCrLf & entity & cbxentity & vbCrLf objScriptValWFStatus.Script = status_script objScriptValWFStatus.TextValue = new_status objListofScriptsWFStatus.Add(objScriptValWFStatus) BRApi.Finance.Data.SetDataCellsUsingMemberScript(si, objListofScriptsWFStatus) Next End If
Return Nothing
End Function #End Region
#Region "RollFwdReq: Roll Forward Requirements" '----------------------------- ' Purpose: Copy selected Current Year requiremnts to Next Year ' ' LOGIC OVERVIEW: ' - Get list of All requirements ' - Reduce list to only selected requirements(BUD_RollFwd_Status = yes) and in current data unit ' - loop thru list of requirements for accounts = BUD_Copy_List.base ' - copy annotations and amounts from source S#T# to target S#T# ' NOTE: data mgmt controls loop of data units you can write to so we loop through target and get data from source ' ' Usage: ' - From Data Mgmt: ' custom calculate Step --> Business Rule = BUD_Main_Calc & Function Name = RollFwdReq ' ' MODIFIED: ' <date> <user id> <JIRA ticket> <change description> ' 2024-03-26 AK RMW-1171 created ' 2024-09-04 AK RMW-15 modified copy to handle 5 years of annual data and a different account list = BUD_Copy_List --> BUD_Rollover_List ' 2025-11-25 AK Tkt-278 / 284 modify copy just PGM annual --> BUD M12 and only Status = L2 completed ' '----------------------------- Public Function RollFwdReq(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As Object Try '========== debug vars ============================================================================================================ Dim sDebugRuleName As String = "BUD_Main_Calc" Dim sDebugFuncName As String = "RollFwdReq"
Dim sCube As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim sTgtScenario As String = api.Pov.Scenario.Name Dim iTgtScenarioYear As Integer = Strings.Right(sTgtScenario,4).XFConvertToInt Dim iSrcScenarioYear As Integer = iTgtScenarioYear Dim sSrcScenario As String = "PGM_C" & iSrcScenarioYear
Dim sCurrTime As String = api.Pov.Time.Name Dim iCurrYear As Integer = Strings.Left(sCurrTime,4).XFConvertToInt
Dim sSrcMbrScript As String = "" Dim sTgtMbrScript As String = ""
Dim sPOVEntity As String = api.Pov.Entity.Name 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": sPOVEntity=" & sPOVEntity & " sTgtScenario=" & sTgtScenario & " iTgtScenarioYear=" & iTgtScenarioYear & " sSrcScenario=" & sSrcScenario & " iSrcScenarioYear=" & iSrcScenarioYear)
' '------------------------------------- ' ' Get All Approved Reqs ' '------------------------------------- Dim lsRollFwdList As New List(Of String)
args.MemberListArgs = New MemberListArgs args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("DimDef", "E#F#U1#U2#U3#U4#U5#U6#") Dim sDataBufferPOVScript="Cb#ARMY:S#" & sSrcScenario & ":T#" & iSrcScenarioYear & ":C#Local:V#Periodic:A#REQ_CMD_App_Req_Amt_ADM:I#Top:O#BeforeAdj:U7#None:U8#None" args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("DataBufferPOVScript", sDataBufferPOVScript) 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": sDataBufferPOVScript=" & sDataBufferPOVScript) 'args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("Time", iYear & ", " & iYear+1 ) args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("Entity", sPOVEntity) args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("Flow", "Command_Requirements.Base.Where(Name doesnotcontain REQ_00)") args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("ReturnList", "True")
lsRollFwdList = BR_GeneralMemberLists.GetFilteredDataRows(si,globals,api,args)
'----- exit if no requirements ----- If lsRollFwdList.Count = 0 Then Return lsRollFwdList
Select Case sCurrTime Case iTgtScenarioYear.ToString & "M12"
'====================================================================================================== ' Copy Annotations '======================================================================================================
'------------------------------------- ' get list of accounts to copy in first year of current scenario '------------------------------------- Dim mbrAcctList As List(Of MemberInfo) = BRApi.Finance.Metadata.GetMembersUsingFilter(si, "A_REQ_Main","A#BUD_Copy_List.base", True) 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": Account List Count=" & mbrAcctList.Count)
'------------------------------------- ' loop thru reqs within data unit '------------------------------------- For Each sRollFwdMbrScript As String In lsRollFwdList Dim sEntity As String = sRollFwdMbrScript.Replace("e#[", "~").Split("~")(1).Replace("]:", "~").Split("~")(0) Dim sFlow As String = sRollFwdMbrScript.Replace("f#[", "~").Split("~")(1).Replace("]:", "~").Split("~")(0)
'--------- Copy BUD annotations from PY to CY --------- For Each mbrAcct As memberInfo In mbrAcctList sSrcMbrScript = "Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sSrcScenario & ":T#" & iSrcScenarioYear & ":C#USD:E#" & sEntity sSrcMbrScript &= ":V#Annotation:A#" & mbrAcct.Member.Name & ":I#None:F#" & sFlow & ":O#BeforeAdj:U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None"
Dim sAcctText As String = api.data.GetDataCellEx(sSrcMbrScript).DataCellAnnotation
sTgtMbrScript = "Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sTgtScenario & ":T#" & iTgtScenarioYear & "M12:C#USD:E#" & sEntity sTgtMbrScript &= ":V#Annotation:A#" & mbrAcct.Member.Name & ":I#None:F#" & sFlow & ":O#BeforeAdj:U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None"
'BRAPI.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": SrcMbrScript=" & sSrcMbrScript & " TgtMbrScript=" & sTgtMbrScript & " Text=" & sAcctText) api.Data.SetDataAttachmentText(sTgtMbrScript, sAcctText, False)
Next

'------------------------------------- ' Clear pre-existing amounts '------------------------------------- 'api.Data.ClearCalculatedData("Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sCurrScenario & ":T#" & sCurrTime & ":C#USD:E#" & sEntity & ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Requested_Amt:F#" & sFlow, True, True, True, True)

'brapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(Si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": sSrcMbrScript = " & sSrcMbrScript) Dim dFundingLine As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCell(sSrcMbrScript).CellAmount 'brapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(Si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": dFundingLine=" & dFundingLine)
'--------- set BUD funding lines --------- sTgtMbrScript = "Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sTgtScenario & ":T#" & iTgtScenarioYear & "M12:C#USD:E#" & sEntity sTgtMbrScript &= ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_PGM_App_Req_Amt:O#Forms:U7#None:U8#None" sTgtMbrScript &= ":I#" & sEntity & ":F#" & sFlow & ":U1#" & sU1 & ":U2#" & sU2 & ":U3#" & sU3 & ":U4#" & sU4 & ":U5#" & sU5 & ":U6#" & sU6
'brapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(Si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": tgtmbrscript = " & sTgtMbrScript & "dFundingLine=" & dFundingLine) If dFundingLine <> 0 Then api.Data.SetDataCell(sTgtMbrScript, dFundingLine, False, True)
Else api.Data.SetDataCell(sTgtMbrScript, 0, True, True) End If 'brapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(Si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": Here99")
Next
Case Else 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": Here99") '------------------------------------- ' loop thru reqs within data unit '------------------------------------- For Each sRollFwdMbrScript As String In lsRollFwdList Dim sEntity As String = sRollFwdMbrScript.Replace("e#[", "~").Split("~")(1).Replace("]:", "~").Split("~")(0) Dim sFlow As String = sRollFwdMbrScript.Replace("f#[", "~").Split("~")(1).Replace("]:", "~").Split("~")(0) Dim sU1 As String = sRollFwdMbrScript.Replace("u1#[", "~").Split("~")(1).Replace("]:", "~").Split("~")(0) Dim sU2 As String = sRollFwdMbrScript.Replace("u2#[", "~").Split("~")(1).Replace("]:", "~").Split("~")(0) Dim sU3 As String = sRollFwdMbrScript.Replace("u3#[", "~").Split("~")(1).Replace("]:", "~").Split("~")(0) Dim sU4 As String = sRollFwdMbrScript.Replace("u4#[", "~").Split("~")(1).Replace("]:", "~").Split("~")(0) Dim sU5 As String = sRollFwdMbrScript.Replace("u5#[", "~").Split("~")(1).Replace("]:", "~").Split("~")(0) Dim sU6 As String = sRollFwdMbrScript.Replace("u6#[", "~").Split("~")(1).Split("]")(0)
'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": E#" & sEntity & ":F#" & sFlow & " POV Scenario=" & api.Pov.Scenario.Name & " POV Time=" & api.Pov.Time.Name & " POV Entity=" & api.Pov.Entity.Name)
'------------------------------------- ' Clear pre-existing amounts '------------------------------------- 'api.Data.ClearCalculatedData("Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sCurrScenario & ":T#" & sCurrTime & ":C#USD:E#" & sEntity & ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Requested_Amt:F#" & sFlow, True, True, True, True)
'--------- get req funding lines --------- sSrcMbrScript = "Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sSrcScenario & ":T#" & iTgtScenarioYear + 1 & ":C#USD:E#" & sEntity
sSrcMbrScript &= ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Requested_Amt:F#" & sFlow & ":I#" & sEntity & ":O#BeforeAdj:U1#" & sU1 & ":U2#" & sU2 & ":U3#" & sU3 & ":U4#" & sU4 & ":U5#" & sU5 & ":U6#" & sU6 & ":U7#None:U8#None" 'BRAPI.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": sSrcMbrScript " & sSrcMbrScript) Dim dFundingLine As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCell(sSrcMbrScript).CellAmount
'--------- set req funding lines --------- sTgtMbrScript = "Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sTgtScenario & ":T#" & iTgtScenarioYear + 1 & "M12:C#USD:E#" & sEntity sTgtMbrScript &= ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_PGM_App_Req_Amt:O#Forms:U7#None:U8#None" sTgtMbrScript &= ":I#" & sEntity & ":F#" & sFlow & ":U1#" & sU1 & ":U2#" & sU2 & ":U3#" & sU3 & ":U4#" & sU4 & ":U5#" & sU5 & ":U6#" & sU6 'BRAPI.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": sTgtMbrScript=" & sTgtMbrScript & " amount = " & dFundingLine)
If dFundingLine <> 0 Then api.Data.SetDataCell(sTgtMbrScript, dFundingLine, False, True)
Else api.Data.SetDataCell(sTgtMbrScript, 0, True, True) End If
