#Region "RollFwdReqSpread: Spread requirements across appropriations on rollover" '----------------------------- ' Purpose: Spread selected Current Year requirements across months, optionally next year M12 ' ' LOGIC OVERVIEW: ' - Get list of all requirements from RollFwdReq ' - Get dictionary<string, list(of integer)> of APPN_L2 spreading ' - Loop thru list of requirements and spread dollars based on APPN dictionary ' - Compile list of APPN_L2 that are tied to reqs and have spread% <> 100 ' - Present APPN_L2 list to users ' ' Usage: ' - From Data Mgmt: ' custom calculate Step --> Business Rule = BUD_Main_Calc & Function Name = RollFwdReqSpread ' ' MODIFIED: ' <date> <user id> <JIRA ticket> <change description> ' 2024-12-04 RD 265 created ' 2025-21-03 AK & MH 958 updated to accomodate obligation and commitment ' '-----------------------------
Private Sub RollFwdReqSpread(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) Try Dim sDebugRuleName As String = "BUD_Main_Calc" Dim sDebugFuncName As String = "BUD_RollFwdReqSpread"
Dim wfProfileName As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).Name Dim WFCube = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim WFScenario As String = ScenarioDimHelper.GetNameFromId(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey) Dim WFYear As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetYearFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey)
'====== SPREAD REQs ======
Dim EntityName As String = api.Pov.Entity.Name Dim TimeName As String = api.Pov.Time.Name
Dim ReqList As New List(Of String)
args.MemberListArgs = New MemberListArgs args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("DimDef", "E#F#U1#U2#U3#U4#U5#U6#") Dim sDataBufferPOVScript="Cb#" + WFCube + ":S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" & WFYear & "M12:C#Local:V#Periodic:A#REQ_PGM_App_Req_Amt:I#Top:O#BeforeAdj:U7#None:U8#None" args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("DataBufferPOVScript", sDataBufferPOVScript) 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": sDataBufferPOVScript=" & sDataBufferPOVScript) args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("Entity", EntityName) args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("Flow", "Command_Requirements.Base.Where(Name doesnotcontain REQ_00)") args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("U1", "Appropriation.Base") args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("ReturnList", "True")
ReqList = BR_GeneralMemberLists.GetFilteredDataRows(si,globals,api,args) 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": EntityName=" & EntityName & ", TimeName=" & TimeName & ", ReqList.Count=" & ReqList.Count )
'------ exit if no requirements ------ If ReqList.Count = 0 Then Exit Sub
For Each Req In ReqList
'====== GET SOURCE INTERSECTION AND AMOUNT ======
Dim SourceIntersection As String = "Cb#" + WFCube + ":S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" + WFYear.ToString + "M12:C#Local:V#Periodic:A#REQ_PGM_App_Req_Amt:I#Top:O#BeforeAdj:U7#None:U8#None:" + Req Dim SourceAmt As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCell(SourceIntersection).CellAmount
'====== GET APPN_FUND AND PARENT APPN_L2 ======
Dim U1Name As String = Strings.Split(SourceIntersection, "u1#[")(1).Split("]")(0) Dim U1DimPk As DimPk = BRApi.Finance.Dim.GetDimPk(si, "U1_APPN_FUND") Dim U1MemberID As Integer = api.Members.GetMemberId(dimType.UD1.Id, U1Name) Dim U1ParentName As String = api.Members.GetParents(U1DimPk, U1MemberId, False, )(0).Name + "_General" 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, U1Name + " " + U1ParentName & " REQ=" & Req)
'====== GET TOTAL PERCENT OBLIG ======
Dim OBL_SpreadYearTotal As String = "Cb#" + WFCube + ":E#" + WFCube + "_General:C#Local:S#" + WFScenario + ":T#" + WFYear.ToString + ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Phased_Obligation_Spread_Prct:F#None:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#" + U1ParentName + ":U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim OBL_SpreadYearTotalPct As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCell(OBL_SpreadYearTotal).CellAmount
Dim OBL_SpreadYearNextM12 As String = "Cb#" + WFCube + ":E#" + WFCube + "_General:C#Local:S#" + WFScenario + ":T#" + (WFYear+1).ToString + "M12:V#Periodic:A#REQ_Phased_Obligation_Spread_Prct:F#None:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#" + U1ParentName + ":U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim OBL_SpreadYearNextM12Pct As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCell(OBL_SpreadYearNextM12).CellAmount
Dim OBL_PercentTotal As Decimal = OBL_SpreadYearTotalPct + OBL_SpreadYearNextM12Pct 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "OBL_PercentTotal: " + OBL_PercentTotal.ToString)
'====== GET MONTHLY PERCENT ======
Dim OBL_SpreadYearMonth As String = "Cb#" + WFCube + ":E#" + WFCube + "_General:C#Local:S#" + WFScenario + ":T#" + TimeName + ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Phased_Obligation_Spread_Prct:F#None:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#" + U1ParentName + ":U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim OBL_SpreadYearMonthPct As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCell(OBL_SpreadYearMonth).CellAmount/100 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "OBL_SpreadYearMonth: " & OBL_SpreadYearMonth)
'====== GET TARGET INTERSECTION ======
Dim OBL_TargetIntersection As String = "Cb#" + WFCube + ":S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" + TimeName + ":C#USD:V#Periodic:A#Phased_Obligation_Base:I#" + EntityName + ":O#Forms:U7#None:U8#None:" + Req Dim OBL_TargetAmt As Decimal 'BRapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "OBL_TargetAmt: " & OBL_TargetAmt)
'====== GET TARGET YEARS FOR FAIL CHECK ======
' Dim TargetYear As String = "Cb#" + WFCube + ":S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" + WFYear.ToString + ":C#USD:V#Periodic:A#REQ_Requested_Amt:I#" + EntityName + ":O#Forms:U7#None:U8#None:" + Req ' Dim TargetYearAmt As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCell(TargetYear).CellAmount ' Dim TargetNextYear As String = "Cb#" + WFCube + ":S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" + (WFYear+1).ToString + ":C#USD:V#Periodic:A#REQ_Requested_Amt:I#" + EntityName + ":O#Forms:U7#None:U8#None:" + Req ' Dim TargetNextYearAmt As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCell(TargetNextYear).CellAmount
' If TargetYearAmt + TargetNextYearAmt <> 0 Then ' Throw New Exception("INFO:" & vbCRLF & vbCRLF & "Spreading already done." & vbCRLF) 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "RD: No Rollover - " + EntityName + TimeName) ' Exit Sub ' End If
'====== SET DATA CELL ====== If OBL_PercentTotal = 100 Then OBL_TargetAmt = Math.Floor(SourceAmt * OBL_SpreadYearMonthPct) api.Data.SetDataCell(OBL_TargetIntersection, OBL_TargetAmt, False) Dim OBL_Outcome As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCell(OBL_TargetIntersection).CellAmount.ToString 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Source Script: " + SourceIntersection + vbCrLf + _ ' "Source Amount: " + SourceAmt.ToString + vbCrLf + _ ' "Month Percent Script: " + OBL_SpreadYearMonth + vbCrLf + _ ' "Month Percent Amount: " + OBL_SpreadYearMonthPct.ToString + vbCrLf + _ ' "Target Script: " + OBL_TargetIntersection + vbCrLf + _ ' "Target Amount: " + OBL_TargetAmt.ToString + vbCrLf + _ ' "Outcome: " + api.Data.GetDataCell(OBL_TargetIntersection).CellAmount.ToString)
Else If OBL_PercentTotal = 0 And TimeName.XFContainsIgnoreCase(WFYear) Then OBL_TargetAmt = Math.Floor(SourceAmt/12) api.Data.SetDataCell(OBL_TargetIntersection, OBL_TargetAmt, False) 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Source Script: " + SourceIntersection + vbCrLf + _ ' "Parent APPNL2: " + U1ParentName + vbCrLf + _ ' "Source Amount: " + SourceAmt.ToString + vbCrLf + _ ' "Total Percent: " + PercentTotal.ToString + vbCrLf + _ ' "Month Script: " + SpreadYearMonth + vbCrLf + _ ' "Month Percent: " + SpreadYearMonthPct.ToString + vbCrLf + _ ' "Target Amount: " + TargetAmt.ToString) Else OBL_TargetAmt = 0 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "FAIL" + vbCrLf + _ ' "Source Script: " + SourceIntersection + vbCrLf + _ ' "Parent APPNL2: " + U1ParentName + vbCrLf + _ ' "Source Amount: " + SourceAmt.ToString + vbCrLf + _ ' "Total Percent: " + PercentTotal.ToString + vbCrLf + _ ' "Month Script: " + SpreadYearMonth + vbCrLf + _ ' "Month Percent: " + SpreadYearMonthPct.ToString + vbCrLf + _ ' "Target Amount: " + TargetAmt.ToString) End If
'====== GET TOTAL PERCENT COMMIT ======
Dim COMMIT_SpreadYearTotal As String = "Cb#" + WFCube + ":E#" + WFCube + "_General:C#Local:S#" + WFScenario + ":T#" + WFYear.ToString + ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Phased_Commitment_Spread_Prct:F#None:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#" + U1ParentName + ":U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim COMMIT_SpreadYearTotalPct As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCell(COMMIT_SpreadYearTotal).CellAmount
Dim COMMIT_SpreadYearNextM12 As String = "Cb#" + WFCube + ":E#" + WFCube + "_General:C#Local:S#" + WFScenario + ":T#" + (WFYear+1).ToString + "M12:V#Periodic:A#REQ_Phased_Commitment_Spread_Prct:F#None:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#" + U1ParentName + ":U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim COMMIT_SpreadYearNextM12Pct As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCell(COMMIT_SpreadYearNextM12).CellAmount
Dim COMMIT_PercentTotal As Decimal = COMMIT_SpreadYearTotalPct + COMMIT_SpreadYearNextM12Pct 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "COMMIT_SpreadYearNextM12: " & COMMIT_SpreadYearNextM12) 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "COMMIT_PercentTotal: " + COMMIT_PercentTotal.ToString)
'====== GET MONTHLY PERCENT ======
Dim COMMIT_SpreadYearMonth As String = "Cb#" + WFCube + ":E#" + WFCube + "_General:C#Local:S#" + WFScenario + ":T#" + TimeName + ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Phased_Commitment_Spread_Prct:F#None:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#" + U1ParentName + ":U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim COMMIT_SpreadYearMonthPct As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCell(COMMIT_SpreadYearMonth).CellAmount/100 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "COMMIT_SpreadYearMonth: " & COMMIT_SpreadYearMonth)
'====== GET TARGET INTERSECTION ======
Dim COMMIT_TargetIntersection As String = "Cb#" + WFCube + ":S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" + TimeName + ":C#USD:V#Periodic:A#Phased_Commitment:I#" + EntityName + ":O#Forms:U7#None:U8#None:" + Req Dim COMMIT_TargetAmt As Decimal 'BRapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "COMMIT_TargetIntersection: " & COMMIT_TargetIntersection)
'====== SET DATA CELL ======
If COMMIT_PercentTotal = 100 Then COMMIT_TargetAmt = Math.Floor(SourceAmt * COMMIT_SpreadYearMonthPct) api.Data.SetDataCell(COMMIT_TargetIntersection, COMMIT_TargetAmt, False) Dim COMMIT_Outcome As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCell(COMMIT_TargetIntersection).CellAmount.ToString 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Source Script: " + SourceIntersection + vbCrLf + _ ' "Source Amount: " + SourceAmt.ToString + vbCrLf + _ ' "Month Percent Script: " + COMMIT_SpreadYearMonth + vbCrLf + _ ' "Month Percent Amount: " + COMMIT_SpreadYearMonthPct.ToString + vbCrLf + _ ' "Target Script: " + COMMIT_TargetIntersection + vbCrLf + _ ' "Target Amount: " + COMMIT_TargetAmt.ToString + vbCrLf + _ ' "Outcome: " + api.Data.GetDataCell(COMMIT_TargetIntersection).CellAmount.ToString) Else If COMMIT_PercentTotal = 0 And TimeName.XFContainsIgnoreCase(WFYear) Then COMMIT_TargetAmt = Math.Floor(SourceAmt/12) api.Data.SetDataCell(COMMIT_TargetIntersection, COMMIT_TargetAmt, False) 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Source Script: " + SourceIntersection + vbCrLf + _ ' "Source Amount: " + SourceAmt.ToString + vbCrLf + _ ' "Month Percent Script: " + COMMIT_SpreadYearMonth + vbCrLf + _ ' "Month Percent Amount: " + COMMIT_SpreadYearMonthPct.ToString + vbCrLf + _ ' "Target Script: " + COMMIT_TargetIntersection + vbCrLf + _ ' "Target Amount: " + COMMIT_TargetAmt.ToString + vbCrLf + _ ' "Outcome: " + api.Data.GetDataCell(COMMIT_TargetIntersection).CellAmount.ToString)
Else COMMIT_TargetAmt = 0 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "FAIL" + vbCrLf + _ ' "Source Script: " + SourceIntersection + vbCrLf + _ ' "Parent APPNL2: " + U1ParentName + vbCrLf + _ ' "Source Amount: " + SourceAmt.ToString + vbCrLf + _ ' "Total Percent: " + PercentTotal.ToString + vbCrLf + _ ' "Month Script: " + SpreadYearMonth + vbCrLf + _ ' "Month Percent: " + SpreadYearMonthPct.ToString + vbCrLf + _ ' "Target Amount: " + TargetAmt.ToString) End If
Next
Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Sub #End Region
#Region "RollFwdReqSpreadRounding: Handle rounding to |WFYear|M12 for requirements spreading" Private Sub RollFwdReqSpreadRounding(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) Try Dim sDebugRuleName As String = "BUD_Main_Calc" Dim sDebugFuncName As String = "BUD_RollFwdReqSpreadRounding"
Dim wfProfileName As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).Name Dim WFCube = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim WFScenario As String = ScenarioDimHelper.GetNameFromId(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey) Dim WFYear As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetYearFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey)
Dim EntityName As String = api.Pov.Entity.Name Dim TimeName As String = api.Pov.Time.Name
Dim ReqList As New List(Of String)
args.MemberListArgs = New MemberListArgs args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("DimDef", "E#F#U1#U2#U3#U4#U5#U6#") Dim sDataBufferPOVScript="Cb#" + WFCube + ":S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" & WFYear & "M12:C#Local:V#Periodic:A#REQ_PGM_App_Req_Amt:I#Top:O#BeforeAdj:U7#None:U8#None" args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("DataBufferPOVScript", sDataBufferPOVScript) 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": sDataBufferPOVScript=" & sDataBufferPOVScript) args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("Entity", EntityName) args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("Flow", "Command_Requirements.Base.Where(Name doesnotcontain REQ_00)") args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("ReturnList", "True")
ReqList = BR_GeneralMemberLists.GetFilteredDataRows(si,globals,api,args) 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": EntityName=" & EntityName & ", TimeName=" & TimeName & ", ReqList.Count=" & ReqList.Count )
'------ exit if no requirements ------ If ReqList.Count = 0 Then Exit Sub
For Each Req In ReqList
Dim SourceIntersection As String = "Cb#" + WFCube + ":S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" + WFYear.ToString + "M12:C#Local:V#Periodic:A#REQ_PGM_App_Req_Amt:I#Top:O#BeforeAdj:U7#None:U8#None:" + Req Dim SourceAmt As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCell(SourceIntersection).CellAmount

#Region "BUD_Copy_to_SpendPlanCall" Public Function CopyBudtoSpendPlan(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As Object Try Dim sEntity As String = api.Pov.Entity.Name Dim sTargetYearMonth As String = api.Pov.Time.Name Dim sTargetScenario As String = api.Pov.Scenario.Name Dim sAPPN As String = args.CustomCalculateArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("APPN") If String.IsNullOrEmpty(sAPPN) Throw New System.Exception(vbCrLf & vbCrLf & "Must select an Appropriation to copy Budget to Spend Plan") End If brapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"Connor's APPN = " & sAPPN) Select Case sAPPN Case "OMA" Me.OMACopyBudtoSpendPlan(si,globals,api,args) Case "OPA" Me.OPACopyBudtoSpendPlan(si,globals,api,args) Case "RDTE" Me.RDTECopyBudtoSpendPlan(si,globals,api,args) End Select

Public Function OMACopyBudtoSpendPlan(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As Object Try
Dim wfCube As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim iWFYear As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetYearFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) Dim prevScenario As String = "BUD_C" & iWFYear Dim sEntity As String = api.Pov.Entity.Name
Dim sTargetYearMonth As String = api.Pov.Time.Name Dim sTargetScenario As String = api.Pov.Scenario.Name Dim sSrcMbrScript As String = "" Dim sTargetMbrScript As String = "" Dim sClearMemberScript As String = "" Dim sClearMemberScript2 As String = "" Dim lAccount As New List (Of String) lAccount.Add("Phased_Obligation_Base") lAccount.Add("Phased_Commitment") For Each sAccount As String In lAccount
'Clear Data sClearMemberScript = "RemoveZeros(Cb#" & wfCube & ":S#" & sTargetScenario & ":T#" & sTargetYearMonth & ":C#USD:E#" & sEntity sClearMemberScript &= ":V#Periodic:A#" & sAccount & ":F#Top:O#BeforeAdj:U2#Top:U4#Top:U5#Top:U7#Top:U8#Top:I#Top)" Dim dbFundingLines As DataBuffer = Nothing Try dbFundingLines = api.Data.GetDataBufferUsingFormula(sClearMemberScript,,False) Catch ex As Exception Throw New System.Exception( "Error: Invalid Source Member Script. sSrcMbrScript=" & sSrcMbrScript) End Try
For Each dbCell As DataBufferCell In dbFundingLines.DataBufferCells.values Dim sU1 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD1Name(api) Dim sU3 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD3Name(api) Dim sU6 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD6Name(api) If sU3.XFContainsIgnoreCase("OMA") sClearMemberScript2 = "Cb#" & wfCube & ":S#" & sTargetScenario & ":T#" & sTargetYearMonth & ":C#USD:E#" & sEntity sClearMemberScript2 &= ":V#Periodic:A#" & sAccount & ":F#Baseline:I#None:U1#"& sU1 & ":U2#None:U3#" & sU3 & ":U4#None:U5#None:U6#" & sU6 & ":U7#None:U8#None" 'brapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"before clear set cell") 'brapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"Clearmemberscript=" & sClearMemberScript2) api.Data.SetDataCell(sClearMemberScript2 & ":O#Import",0, False, True) api.Data.SetDataCell(sClearMemberScript2 & ":O#Forms",0, False, True) End If Next
'Set Cells sSrcMbrScript = "RemoveZeros(Cb#" & wfCube & ":S#" & prevScenario & ":T#" & sTargetYearMonth & ":C#Aggregated:E#" & sEntity.Replace("_General","") sSrcMbrScript &= ":V#Periodic:A#" & sAccount & ":F#Top:O#BeforeAdj:U2#Top:U4#Top:U5#Top:U7#Top:U8#Top:I#Top)"
Try dbFundingLines = api.Data.GetDataBufferUsingFormula(sSrcMbrScript,,False) Catch ex As Exception Throw New System.Exception( "Error: Invalid Source Member Script. sSrcMbrScript=" & sSrcMbrScript) End Try
Dim dictionaryCells As New Dictionary (Of String, Long)
For Each dbCell As DataBufferCell In dbFundingLines.DataBufferCells.values Dim sU1 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD1Name(api) Dim sU3 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD3Name(api) Dim sU6 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD6Name(api) If sU3.XFContainsIgnoreCase("OMA") Then
Dim Amount As Long = dbCell.cellamount
Dim sParentAPESix As String = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetParents(si, BRApi.Finance.Dim.GetDimPk(si, "U3_APE_PT"), BRapi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si,dimtype.UD3.Id, sU3), False)(0).Name
Dim sParentSAG As String = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetParents(si, BRApi.Finance.Dim.GetDimPk(si, "U3_APE"), BRapi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si,dimtype.UD3.Id, sParentAPESix), False)(0).Name
If sU6.XFContainsIgnoreCase("None") Then sU6 = "ABO_07" Else If sU6.XFContainsIgnoreCase("ALLOBJ") Then sU6 = "ABO_07" Else Dim lCommodity As List(Of MemberInfo) = BRApi.Finance.Metadata.GetMembersUsingFilter(si,"U6_CommitmentItem","U6#" & sU6 & ".Ancestors",True) For Each sCommodity As MemberInfo In lCommodity If sCommodity.Member.Name.XFContainsIgnoreCase("ABO_") Then sU6 = sCommodity.Member.Name Exit For End If Next End If Dim sKey As String = "U1#" & sU1 & ":U3#" & sParentSAG & ":U6#" & sU6
If dictionaryCells.ContainsKey(sKey) Then dictionaryCells(sKey) += Amount Else dictionaryCells.Add(sKey, Amount) End If
End If Next
For Each Kvp As KeyValuePair(Of String, Long) In dictionaryCells
Dim array = Kvp.Key.Split(":") Dim sU1 As String = array(0) Dim sU3 As String = array(1) Dim sU6 As String = array(2)
Dim sU3APENINE As String = BRApi.Finance.Metadata.GetMembersUsingFilter(si,"U3_APE_PT",sU3 & ".Base.Where(text8 contains SpendPlan)",True)(0).Member.Name
sTargetMbrScript = "Cb#" & wfCube & ":S#" & sTargetScenario & ":T#" & sTargetYearMonth & ":C#USD:E#" & sEntity sTargetMbrScript &= ":V#Periodic:A#" & sAccount & ":F#Baseline:O#Import:I#None:"& sU1 & ":U2#None:U3#" & sU3APENINE & ":U4#None:U5#None:" & sU6 & ":U7#None:U8#None"
api.Data.SetDataCell(sTargetMbrScript,kvp.Value, False, True)
Next
Next 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"OMA") Return Nothing Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function #End Region
#Region "OPACopyBudtoSpendPlan"
Public Function OPACopyBudtoSpendPlan(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As Object Try
Dim wfCube As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim iWFYear As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetYearFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) Dim prevScenario As String = "BUD_C" & iWFYear Dim sEntity As String = api.Pov.Entity.Name Dim sTargetYearMonth As String = api.Pov.Time.Name Dim sTargetScenario As String = api.Pov.Scenario.Name Dim sSrcMbrScript As String = "" Dim sTargetMbrScript As String = "" Dim sClearMemberScript As String = "" Dim sClearMemberScript2 As String = ""
'Clear Data sClearMemberScript = "RemoveZeros(Cb#" & wfCube & ":S#" & sTargetScenario & ":T#" & sTargetYearMonth & ":C#USD:E#" & sEntity sClearMemberScript &= ":V#Periodic:A#Phased_Obligation_Base:F#Top:O#BeforeAdj:U5#Top:U7#Top:U8#Top:I#Top)" Dim dbFundingLines As DataBuffer = Nothing Try dbFundingLines = api.Data.GetDataBufferUsingFormula(sClearMemberScript,,False) Catch ex As Exception Throw New System.Exception( "Error: Invalid Source Member Script. sSrcMbrScript=" & sSrcMbrScript) End Try
For Each dbCell As DataBufferCell In dbFundingLines.DataBufferCells.values Dim sU1 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD1Name(api) Dim sU2 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD2Name(api) Dim sU3 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD3Name(api) Dim sU4 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD4Name(api) Dim sU6 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD6Name(api) If sU3.XFContainsIgnoreCase("OPA") sClearMemberScript2 = "Cb#" & wfCube & ":S#" & sTargetScenario & ":T#" & sTargetYearMonth & ":C#USD:E#" & sEntity sClearMemberScript2 &= ":V#Periodic:A#Phased_Obligation_Base:F#Baseline:U2#" & sU2 & ":U4#" & sU4 & ":U5#None:U7#None:U8#None:I#None:U1#"& sU1 & ":U3#" & sU3 & ":U6#" & sU6 'brapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"OPA" & sClearMemberScript2) api.Data.SetDataCell(sClearMemberScript2 & ":O#Import",0, False, True) api.Data.SetDataCell(sClearMemberScript2 & ":O#Forms",0, False, True) End If Next
'Copy Data sSrcMbrScript = "RemoveZeros(Cb#" & wfCube & ":S#" & prevScenario & ":T#" & sTargetYearMonth & ":C#Aggregated:E#" & sEntity.Replace("_General","") sSrcMbrScript &= ":V#Periodic:A#Phased_Obligation_Base:F#Top:O#BeforeAdj:U5#Top:U7#Top:U8#Top:I#Top)"
Try dbFundingLines = api.Data.GetDataBufferUsingFormula(sSrcMbrScript,,False) Catch ex As Exception Throw New System.Exception( "Error: Invalid Source Member Script. sSrcMbrScript=" & sSrcMbrScript) End Try
Dim dictionaryCells As New Dictionary (Of String, Long)
For Each dbCell As DataBufferCell In dbFundingLines.DataBufferCells.values Dim sU1 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD1Name(api) Dim sU2 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD2Name(api) Dim sU3 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD3Name(api) Dim sU4 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD4Name(api) Dim sU6 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD6Name(api) If sU3.XFContainsIgnoreCase("OPA") Then
Dim Amount As Long = dbCell.cellamount
Dim sParentAPESix As String = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetParents(si, BRApi.Finance.Dim.GetDimPk(si, "U3_APE_PT"), BRapi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si,dimtype.UD3.Id, sU3), False)(0).Name If sU6.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("None") sU6 = "ALLOBJ" Else If sU6.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("ALLOBJ") sU6 = "ALLOBJ" Else Dim lCommodity As List(Of MemberInfo) = BRApi.Finance.Metadata.GetMembersUsingFilter(si,"U6_CommitmentItem","U6#" & sU6 & ".Ancestors",True) For Each sCommodity As MemberInfo In lCommodity Select Case sCommodity.Member.Name Case "ABO_01" sU6 = sCommodity.Member.Name Case "ABO_04" sU6 = sCommodity.Member.Name Case "ABO_07" sU6 = "ALLOBJ" Case "ABO_02" sU6 = "ALLOBJ" End Select Next End If Dim sKey As String = "U1#" & sU1 & ":U2#" & sU2 & ":U3#" & sParentAPESix & ":U4#" & sU4 & ":U6#" & sU6
If dictionaryCells.ContainsKey(sKey) Then dictionaryCells(sKey) += Amount Else dictionaryCells.Add(sKey, Amount) End If
End If Next
For Each Kvp As KeyValuePair(Of String, Long) In dictionaryCells
Dim array = Kvp.Key.Split(":") Dim sU1 As String = array(0) Dim sU2 As String = array(1) Dim sU3 As String = array(2) Dim sU4 As String = array(3) Dim sU6 As String = array(4)
Dim sU3APENINE As String = BRApi.Finance.Metadata.GetMembersUsingFilter(si,"U3_APE_PT",sU3 & ".Base.Where(text8 contains SpendPlan)",True)(0).Member.Name
sTargetMbrScript = "Cb#" & wfCube & ":S#" & sTargetScenario & ":T#" & sTargetYearMonth & ":C#USD:E#" & sEntity sTargetMbrScript &= ":V#Periodic:A#Phased_Obligation_Base:F#Baseline:O#Import:" & sU2 & ":" & sU4 & ":U5#None:U7#None:U8#None:I#None:"& sU1 & ":U3#" & sU3APENINE & ":" & sU6
api.Data.SetDataCell(sTargetMbrScript,kvp.Value, False, True)
Next
Return Nothing Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function #End Region
#Region "RDTECopyBudtoSpendPlan"
Public Function RDTECopyBudtoSpendPlan(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As Object Try
Dim wfCube As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim iWFYear As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetYearFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) Dim prevScenario As String = "BUD_C" & iWFYear Dim sEntity As String = api.Pov.Entity.Name Dim sTargetYearMonth As String = api.Pov.Time.Name Dim sTargetScenario As String = api.Pov.Scenario.Name Dim sSrcMbrScript As String = "" Dim sTargetMbrScript As String = "" Dim sClearMemberScript As String = "" Dim sClearMemberScript2 As String = ""
'Clear Data sClearMemberScript = "RemoveZeros(Cb#" & wfCube & ":S#" & sTargetScenario & ":T#" & sTargetYearMonth & ":C#USD:E#" & sEntity sClearMemberScript &= ":V#Periodic:A#Phased_Obligation_Base:F#Top:O#BeforeAdj:U5#Top:U7#Top:U8#Top:I#Top)" Dim dbFundingLines As DataBuffer = Nothing Try dbFundingLines = api.Data.GetDataBufferUsingFormula(sClearMemberScript,,False) Catch ex As Exception Throw New System.Exception( "Error: Invalid Source Member Script. sSrcMbrScript=" & sSrcMbrScript) End Try
For Each dbCell As DataBufferCell In dbFundingLines.DataBufferCells.values Dim sU1 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD1Name(api) Dim sU2 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD2Name(api) Dim sU3 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD3Name(api) Dim sU4 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD4Name(api) Dim sU6 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD6Name(api) If sU3.XFContainsIgnoreCase("RDTE") sClearMemberScript2 = "Cb#" & wfCube & ":S#" & sTargetScenario & ":T#" & sTargetYearMonth & ":C#USD:E#" & sEntity sClearMemberScript2 &= ":V#Periodic:A#Phased_Obligation_Base:F#Baseline:U2#" & sU2 & ":U4#" & sU4 & ":U5#None:U7#None:U8#None:I#None:U1#"& sU1 & ":U3#" & sU3 & ":U6#" & sU6
'brapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"RDTE " & sClearMemberScript2) api.Data.SetDataCell(sClearMemberScript2 & ":O#Import",0, False, True) api.Data.SetDataCell(sClearMemberScript2 & ":O#Forms",0, False, True) End If Next
sSrcMbrScript = "RemoveZeros(Cb#" & wfCube & ":S#" & prevScenario & ":T#" & sTargetYearMonth & ":C#Aggregated:E#" & sEntity.Replace("_General","") sSrcMbrScript &= ":V#Periodic:A#Phased_Obligation_Base:F#Top:O#BeforeAdj:U5#Top:U7#Top:U8#Top:I#Top)"
Try dbFundingLines = api.Data.GetDataBufferUsingFormula(sSrcMbrScript,,False) Catch ex As Exception Throw New System.Exception( "Error: Invalid Source Member Script. sSrcMbrScript=" & sSrcMbrScript) End Try
Dim dictionaryCells As New Dictionary (Of String, Long)
For Each dbCell As DataBufferCell In dbFundingLines.DataBufferCells.values Dim sU1 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD1Name(api) Dim sU2 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD2Name(api) Dim sU3 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD3Name(api) Dim sU4 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD4Name(api) Dim sU6 As String = dbCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD6Name(api) If sU3.XFContainsIgnoreCase("RDTE") Then
Dim Amount As Long = dbCell.cellamount If sU6.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("None") sU6 = "ALLOBJ" Else If sU6.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("ALLOBJ") sU6 = "ALLOBJ" Else Dim lCommodity As List(Of MemberInfo) = BRApi.Finance.Metadata.GetMembersUsingFilter(si,"U6_CommitmentItem","U6#" & sU6 & ".Ancestors",True) For Each sCommodity As MemberInfo In lCommodity Select Case sCommodity.Member.Name Case "ABO_01" sU6 = sCommodity.Member.Name Case "ABO_04" sU6 = sCommodity.Member.Name Case "ABO_07" sU6 = "ALLOBJ" Case "ABO_02" sU6 = "ALLOBJ"
End Select Next End If Dim sKey As String = "U1#" & sU1 & ":U2#" & sU2 & ":U3#" & sU3 & ":U4#" & sU4 & ":U6#" & sU6
If dictionaryCells.ContainsKey(sKey) Then dictionaryCells(sKey) += Amount Else dictionaryCells.Add(sKey, Amount) End If
End If Next
For Each Kvp As KeyValuePair(Of String, Long) In dictionaryCells
Dim array = Kvp.Key.Split(":") Dim sU1 As String = array(0) Dim sU2 As String = array(1) Dim sU3 As String = array(2) Dim sU4 As String = array(3) Dim sU6 As String = array(4)
sTargetMbrScript = "Cb#" & wfCube & ":S#" & sTargetScenario & ":T#" & sTargetYearMonth & ":C#USD:E#" & sEntity sTargetMbrScript &= ":V#Periodic:A#Phased_Obligation_Base:F#Baseline:O#Import:" & sU2 & ":" & sU4 & ":U5#None:U7#None:U8#None:I#None:"& sU1 & ":" & sU3 & ":" & sU6
api.Data.SetDataCell(sTargetMbrScript,kvp.Value, False, True)
Next
Return Nothing Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function #End Region

Imports System Imports System.Collections.Generic Imports System.Data Imports System.Data.Common Imports System.Globalization Imports System.IO Imports System.Linq Imports Microsoft.VisualBasic Imports OneStream.Finance.Database Imports OneStream.Finance.Engine Imports OneStream.Shared.Common Imports OneStream.Shared.Database Imports OneStream.Shared.Engine Imports OneStream.Shared.Wcf Imports OneStream.Stage.Database Imports OneStream.Stage.Engine Imports OneStreamWorkspacesApi Imports OneStreamWorkspacesApi.V800
'BUD_Member_List Namespace OneStream.BusinessRule.Finance.CMD_SPLN_Mbr_Lists Public Class MainClass ' Public Sub New() ' Function CreateProperty ' Property financeArgs As New FinanceRulesArgs ' End Sub Public Function Main(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As Object Try
'========== debug vars ============================================================================================================ Dim sDebugRuleName As String = "BUD_Member_Lists" Dim sDebugFuncName As String = "Main"
#Region "Onestream Default Function" Select Case api.FunctionType
Case Is = FinanceFunctionType.MemberListHeaders 'Dim objMemberListHeaders As New List(Of MemberListHeader) 'objMemberListHeaders.Add(new MemberListHeader("Sample Member List")) 'Return objMemberListHeaders
Case Is = FinanceFunctionType.MemberList 'Example: E#Root.CustomMemberList(BRName=MyBusinessRuleName, MemberListName=[Sample Member List], Name1=Value1) 'If args.MemberListArgs.MemberListName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("Sample Member List") Then 'Dim objMemberListHeader As New MemberListHeader(args.MemberListArgs.MemberListName) 'Dim objMemberInfos As List(Of MemberInfo) = api.Members.GetMembersUsingFilter(args.MemberListArgs.DimPk, "E#Root.Base", Nothing) 'Dim objMemberList As New MemberList(objMemberListHeader, objMemberInfos) 'Return objMemberList 'End If #End Region
If args.MemberListArgs.MemberListName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("GetFirstMDEPYOYGrowthRows") Then #Region "GetFirstMDEPYOYGrowthRows" Dim sRowMbrList As String = String.Join(",",Me.GetFirstMDEPYOYGrowthRows(si,globals,api,args))
If sRowMbrList = "" Then Return Nothing Else Dim objMemberListHeader As New MemberListHeader(args.MemberListArgs.MemberListName) Dim objMemberInfos As List(Of MemberInfo) = api.Members.GetMembersUsingFilter(args.MemberListArgs.DimPk, sRowMbrList , Nothing) Dim objMemberList As New MemberList(objMemberListHeader, objMemberInfos) Return objMemberList
End If #End Region End If
If args.MemberListArgs.MemberListName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("GetBUDRankedList") Then #Region "GetBUDRankedList"
'Dim tStart As DateTime = Date.Now() Dim oBUDList = Me.GetBUDRankedList(si,globals,api,args) If oBUDList Is Nothing Then Return Nothing Dim sRowMbrList As String = String.Join(",",oBUDList)
If sRowMbrList = "" Then Return Nothing Else
Dim objMemberListHeader As New MemberListHeader(args.MemberListArgs.MemberListName)
Dim objMemberInfos As List(Of MemberInfo) = api.Members.GetMembersUsingFilter(args.MemberListArgs.DimPk, sRowMbrList , Nothing)
Dim objMemberList As New MemberList(objMemberListHeader, objMemberInfos)
'Dim tStop As DateTime = Date.Now() 'Dim tDuration As TimeSpan = tStop.Subtract(tStart) 'Dim sDebug As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("Debug").Trim 'If sDebug.XFContainsIgnoreCase("DebugCubeView") Then BRapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebug & ": " & args.MemberListArgs.MemberListName & " took " & tDuration.TotalSeconds.ToString("0.0000"))
Return objMemberList 'BRapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"Line64") End If
#End Region End If
If args.MemberListArgs.MemberListName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("GetBUD_IC") Then #Region "GetBUD_IC" Dim sIC As String = Me.GetBUD_IC(si,globals,api,args)
If sIC = "" Then Return Nothing Else Dim objMemberListHeader As New MemberListHeader(args.MemberListArgs.MemberListName) Dim objMemberInfos As List(Of MemberInfo) = api.Members.GetMembersUsingFilter(args.MemberListArgs.DimPk, sIC , Nothing) Dim objMemberList As New MemberList(objMemberListHeader, objMemberInfos)
Return objMemberList End If #End Region End If
If args.MemberListArgs.MemberListName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("GetBUDListByStatus") Then #Region "Get BUD List by Status" Dim tStart As DateTime = Date.Now() Dim lsDimMbrs = Me.GetDimMbrsList(si,globals,api,args)
If lsDimMbrs Is Nothing Then Return Nothing Dim objMemberListHeader As New MemberListHeader(args.MemberListArgs.MemberListName) Dim objMemberInfos As List(Of MemberInfo) = api.Members.GetMembersUsingFilter(args.MemberListArgs.DimPk, String.Join(",",lsDimMbrs) , Nothing)
Dim objMemberList As New MemberList(objMemberListHeader, objMemberInfos)
Return objMemberList
Dim tStop As DateTime = Date.Now() Dim tDuration As TimeSpan = tStop.Subtract(tStart) BRapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, args.MemberListArgs.MemberListName & " took " & tDuration.TotalSeconds.ToString("0.0000"))
#End Region End If
If args.MemberListArgs.MemberListName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("GetDimMbrsListReviseREQsByTarget") Then #Region "Get Dimensional Mbrs List - Revise REQs By Target" '================================================================================================================================================================================================================================================= '== WARNING: This method is used specifically for the Revise REQs By Target Linked Dashboard '== This method is used to return row headers for the Formulator to revise REQs' amount to match Funding Target '== - Note: This function calls DataSet Rule BUD_DataSet > GetDimMbrsDataSet to search for specific inputted single member for each of the following dim: Entity, UD1, UD2, UD3 and return only Requirements with funding lines of this combination with the correct Formulation statuses '== - Note: This function then parse through the data table to return a list of rowheaders '== - Note: This function also caches the resulting row headers to use to calculate total amounts on Cube View '=================================================================================================================================================================================================================================================
'Dim tStart As DateTime = Date.Now() Dim lsDimMbrs = Me.GetDimMbrsListReviseREQsByTarget(si,globals,api,args) If lsDimMbrs Is Nothing Then Return Nothing Dim sCacheName As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("CacheName").Trim
'----- store row headers to user session variable ----- Dim sRowMbrList As String = String.Join(",", lsDimMbrs) If sCacheName <> "" Then BRApi.Utilities.SetWorkspaceSessionSetting(si, si.UserName, "BUD_FilteredDataRows", sCacheName, sRowMbrList)
'----- return memberlist Dim objMemberListHeader As New MemberListHeader(args.MemberListArgs.MemberListName) Dim objMemberInfos As List(Of MemberInfo) = api.Members.GetMembersUsingFilter(args.MemberListArgs.DimPk, sRowMbrList, Nothing)
Dim objMemberList As New MemberList(objMemberListHeader, objMemberInfos)
'Dim tStop As DateTime = Date.Now() 'Dim tDuration As TimeSpan = tStop.Subtract(tStart) 'BRapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, args.MemberListArgs.MemberListName & " took " & tDuration.TotalSeconds.ToString("0.0000"))
Return objMemberList #End Region End If
If args.MemberListArgs.MemberListName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("GetREQFundingAmtDataRows") Then #Region "Get REQ Funding Amounts Data Rows" '========================================================================================================================================================================================================================================= '== WARNING: This method is used specifically for the Requirement Details / Update Requirement '== This method is used to cache the memberscript and amounts for the REQ. The Cached info will then be used to rewrite the amount if the User initiate a save and the save fails commitment vs obligation check '== This method calls General_Member_Lists - GetFilteredDataRows to get the row headers that will be returned to the CV, then use the info and the DataBufferPOVScript get the datacell amt '== Example Call from Cube View: BUD_Funding_Month_Amt '== - U1#Root.CustomMemberList( '== BRName=BUD_Member_Lists, '== MemberListName=GetREQFundingAmtDataRows, '== CacheName=BUD_Funding_Month_Amt, '== ScriptAmtCacheName=|!param_BUDPRO_AAAAAA_REQScriptAmtCacheName__Shared!|, '== ReturnList=True, '== DimDef=A#U1#U2#U3#U4#U5#U6#, '== DataBufferPOVScript=[Cb#|WFCube|:S#|WFScenario|:C#Local:V#Periodic:F#XFBR(BUD_String_Helper, TitleParseFlow, title = |!prompt_cbx_BUDPRO_AAAAAA_BUDListByEntity__Shared_UpdateReq!|):O#BeforeAdj:U7#None:U8#None], '== Entity=E#XFBR(BUD_String_Helper, TitleParseEntity, title = |!prompt_cbx_BUDPRO_AAAAAA_BUDListByEntity__Shared_UpdateReq!|), '== Time=[T#|WFTime|.Base, '== T#|WFTime|, '== T#|WFYearNext|M12], '== Account=[Phased_Obligation_Base,Phased_Commitment] '== ) '========================================================================================================================================================================================================================================== Dim lsDimMbrs = Me.GetREQFundingAmtDataRows(si,globals,api,args) If lsDimMbrs Is Nothing Then Return Nothing
'----- return memberlist Dim objMemberListHeader As New MemberListHeader(args.MemberListArgs.MemberListName) Dim objMemberInfos As List(Of MemberInfo) = api.Members.GetMembersUsingFilter(args.MemberListArgs.DimPk, String.Join(",", lsDimMbrs), Nothing)
Dim objMemberList As New MemberList(objMemberListHeader, objMemberInfos)
Return objMemberList
#End Region End If

'================================================================================================================================================== '========== get BUDs that have data based on Filters using General_Member_lists =================================================================== '==================================================================================================================================================

lsMasterDimList = BR_GeneralMemberLists.GetFilteredDataRows(si,globals,api,args) 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": lsMasterDimList=" & String.Join(", " , lsMasterDimList))
Dim lsDimMbrs As New List(Of String) For Each x As String In lsAllBUDList For Each y As String In lsMasterDimList If y.Contains(x) Then If sDimDef.XFContainsIgnoreCase("E#F#") Then lsDimMbrs.Add(y) Else lsDimMbrs.Add(y.Replace($"{x}:","")) End If End If Next Next 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": sScenario=" & sScenario & " lsDimMbrs=" & String.Join(", " , lsDimMbrs))
If lsDimMbrs.Count = 0 Then Return lsDimMbrs End If lsDimMbrs = lsDimMbrs.Distinct().ToList() BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "BUD_Mbr End" & Date.Now().ToString("hh:mm:ss:fff")) Return lsDimMbrs

#Region "GetAllBUDListReapplyInflation" '--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ' PURPOSE: return list of all E#F# requirements - searches data attachment table where BUD_Title is not blank ' ' LOGIC OVERVIEW: ' - SQL query against table = DATAATTACHMENT where BUD_Title is not empty ' - return list of E#F# ' ' USAGE: ' -Used to get All BUDs for Reapply Inflation Rates calculation in REQ_Main_Calc ' MODIFIED: '10/3/24 - Created by JM '--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- Public Function GetAllBUDListReapplyInflation(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As List(Of String) Try '================================================================================================================================================== '========== workflow vars ========================================================================================================================= '================================================================================================================================================== Dim sCube As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim sCurrScenario As String = ScenarioDimHelper.GetNameFromId(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey) Dim iCurrWFYear As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetYearFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey)
Dim sTitleScenario As String = sCurrScenario Dim sTitleYear As String = iCurrWFYear.ToString
Dim lsEntity As New List(Of String) Dim lsFlow As New List(Of String)
Dim sEntityMbrfilter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("EntityMbrFilter").trim Dim sFlowMbrFilter As String = "Command_Requirements.Base.Where(Name doesnotcontain REQ_00)" Dim sDimDef As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("ReturnDim").trim Dim sMode As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("Mode").trim Dim sTitleSearch As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("TitleSearch","")
Dim sScenario As String = sCurrScenario Dim iYear As Integer = iCurrWFYear Select Case True Case sMode.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("Current") sScenario = sCurrScenario iYear = iCurrWFYear End Select
'================================================================================================================================================== '========== get BUD return list ================================================================================================================= '================================================================================================================================================== Dim SQL As New Text.StringBuilder SQL.Append("Select CUBE, SCENARIO, TIME, CONS, ENTITY, FLOW From DATAATTACHMENT Where ACCOUNT = 'REQ_Title' And CUBE = '" & sCube & "' And CONS = 'USD' And SCENARIO = '" & sScenario & "' And TIME = '" & iYear.ToString & "'") If Not String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(sTitleSearch) Then SQL.Append($" AND TEXT LIKE '%{sTitleSearch}%'") End If
Dim dtReapply As DataTable Using dbConn As DbConnInfo = BRApi.Database.CreateApplicationDbConnInfo(si) dtReapply = BRApi.Database.ExecuteSql(dbConn,SQL.ToString(),True) End Using '================================================================================================================================================== '========== build BUD return list ================================================================================================================= '==================================================================================================================================================
Dim mbrEntityList = sEntityMbrfilter Dim lsAllBUDList As New List( Of String) If dtReapply.Rows.Count > 0 Then For Each drReq As DataRow In dtReapply.Rows '---- reduce list to only entities within filter ----- lsAllBUDList.Add($"E#[{drReq("Entity")}]:F#[{drReq("Flow")}]".ToLower)
Next
End If
'Check if loop output values If lsAllBUDList.Count = 0 Then lsAllBUDList.Add("E#[None]:F#[None]") Return lsAllBUDList End If '================================================================================================================================================== '========== get BUDs that have data based on Filters using General_Member_lists =================================================================== '==================================================================================================================================================
Dim lsMasterDimList As New List( Of String) If String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(sDimDef) Then Return lsAllBUDList Else
If sDimDef.XFContainsIgnoreCase("E#") And sDimDef.XFContainsIgnoreCase("F#") Then sDimDef = "E#F#" & sDimDef.Replace("E#","").Replace("F#","") args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("DimDef", sDimDef) Else args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("DimDef", "E#F#" & sDimDef) End If
Dim sDataBufferPOVScript="Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sScenario & ":C#Local:V#Periodic:A#REQ_Requested_Amt:I#Top:O#BeforeAdj:U5#Top:U6#Top:U7#None:U8#None"
args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("Time", iYear & ", " & iYear+1 & ", " & iYear+2 & ", " & iYear+3 & ", " & iYear+4 ) args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("Entity", sEntityMbrfilter) args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("Flow", sFlowMbrFilter) args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("ReturnList", "True") Dim sIC As String = "" If args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.ContainsKey("IC") Then sIC = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("IC").trim args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("IC", sIC) End If
Dim sEntityFilter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("EntityFilter").trim
Dim U1Filter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("U1Filter").trim If String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(U1Filter) Then sDataBufferPOVScript &= ":U1#Top"
Dim U2Filter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("U2Filter").trim If String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(U2Filter) Then sDataBufferPOVScript &= ":U2#Top"
Dim U3ParentFilter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("U3ParentFilter").trim
Dim U3Filter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("U3Filter").trim
If String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(U3Filter) And String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(U3ParentFilter) Then sDataBufferPOVScript &= ":U3#Top"
Dim U4Filter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("U4Filter").trim If String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(U4Filter) Then sDataBufferPOVScript &= ":U4#Top"
If args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.ContainsKey("ICFilter") Then Dim sICFilter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("ICFilter").trim args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("ICFilter", sICFilter) End If
args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("DataBufferPOVScript", sDataBufferPOVScript) lsMasterDimList = BR_GeneralMemberLists.GetFilteredDataRows(si,globals,api,args)
'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": lsMasterDimList=" & String.Join(", " , lsMasterDimList)) End If
Dim lsDimMbrs As New List(Of String) For Each x As String In lsAllBUDList For Each y As String In lsMasterDimList If y.Contains(x) Then If sDimDef.XFContainsIgnoreCase("E#F#") Then lsDimMbrs.Add(y) Else lsDimMbrs.Add(y.Replace($"{x}:","")) End If End If Next Next
If lsDimMbrs.Count = 0 Then lsDimMbrs.Add("E#[None]:F#[None]") Return lsDimMbrs End If lsDimMbrs = lsDimMbrs.Distinct().ToList() Return lsDimMbrs
Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function #End Region

Select Case column ' Case "A" ' sMbrScript &= "A#[" & row(column) & "]" Case "Flow" sMbrScript &= "F#[" & row(column) & "]" Case "U4" sMbrScript &= "U4#[" & api.Members.GetMemberName(dimtype.UD4.Id, row(column)) & "]" Case "U5" sMbrScript &= "U5#[" & api.Members.GetMemberName(dimtype.UD5.Id, row(column)) & "]" Case "U6" sMbrScript &= "U6#[" & api.Members.GetMemberName(dimtype.UD6.Id, row(column)) & "]" End Select Next 'Set empty dim value to None. #Region "GetFilteredRowsTotal"
Public Function GetFilteredRowsTotal(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As DataCell Try '========== debug vars ============================================================================================================ Dim sDebugFuncName As String = "GetFilteredRowsTotal" '========== workflow vars ============================================================================================================ 'Dim wfProfileName As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).Name Dim wfCube = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName 'Dim wfScenarioName As String = ScenarioDimHelper.GetNameFromId(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey) 'Dim wfScenarioTypeID As Integer = BRApi.Finance.Scenario.GetScenarioType(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey).Id Dim wfTimeName As String = BRApi.Finance.Time.GetNameFromId(si,si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) Dim iWFYear As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetYearFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) 'Dim iWFMonth As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetMonthIdFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) Dim sMode As String = args.DataCellArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("Mode","").Trim '----- get list of row headers from user session variable ----- Dim sCacheRowNames As String = args.DataCellArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("CacheName","").Trim If sCacheRowNames = "" Then Return Nothing
Dim aCacheRowNames As String() = sCacheRowNames.Split(",")
Dim sRowHeaders As String = ""
For Each sCacheName As String In aCacheRowNames If sCacheName.trim = "" Then Continue For If sRowHeaders = "" Then sRowHeaders = BRApi.Utilities.GetWorkspaceSessionSetting(si, si.UserName, "BUD_FilteredDataRows", sCacheName, "") Else sRowHeaders &= "," & BRApi.Utilities.GetWorkspaceSessionSetting(si, si.UserName, "BUD_FilteredDataRows", sCacheName, "") End If Next
If sRowHeaders.Trim = "" Then Return Nothing
Dim asRowsHeaders As String() = sRowHeaders.Split(",")
Dim sGetDataCellScript As String = "" Dim total As Decimal If sMode = "" Then For Each sHeader As String In asRowsHeaders total = total + api.Data.GetDataCell(sHeader).CellAmount 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Cache: " & sHeader & " = " & api.Data.GetDataCell(sHeader).CellAmount & " ,Total = " & total & " ,acc = " & api.Pov.Account.Name) Next ElseIf sMode = "TotalAll" Then For Each sHeader As String In asRowsHeaders total = total + api.Data.GetDataCell(sHeader & ":T#" & iWFYear).CellAmount total = total + api.Data.GetDataCell(sHeader & ":T#" & (iWFYear + 1) & "M12").CellAmount Next End If
Dim cellPK As DataCellPk = api.pov.GetDataCellPk Dim cell As DataCell = New DataCell(cellPk, total, DataCellStatus.CreateDataCellStatus(False, False))
Return cell
Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function #End Region
#Region "Get REQ Funding Amounts Data Rows" '=================================================================================================================================================================================================================================== '== WARNING: This method is used specifically for the Requirement Details / Update Requirement '== This method is used to cache the memberscript and amounts for the REQ. The Cached info will then be used to rewrite the amount if the User initiate a save and the save fails commitment vs obligation check '== This method calls General_Member_Lists - GetFilteredDataRows to get the row headers that will be returned to the CV, then use the info and the DataBufferPOVScript get the datacell amt '===================================================================================================================================================================================================================================
Public Function GetREQFundingAmtDataRows(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As List(Of String) Try Dim wfCube = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim wfScenarioName As String = ScenarioDimHelper.GetNameFromId(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey) Dim wfTimeName As String = BRApi.Finance.Time.GetNameFromId(si,si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) Dim iWFYear As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetYearFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) Dim sDataBufferPOVScript As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("DataBufferPOVScript").Trim Dim sEntity As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("Entity").Trim Dim sIC As String = sEntity.Replace("E#","I#") If Not sDataBufferPOVScript.XFContainsIgnoreCase("E#") Then sDataBufferPOVScript &= $":{sEntity}" If Not sDataBufferPOVScript.XFContainsIgnoreCase("I#") Then sDataBufferPOVScript &= $":{sIC}" Dim sScriptAmtCacheName As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("ScriptAmtCacheName").Trim Dim dt As New DataTable(sScriptAmtCacheName) dt.Columns.Add("Script", GetType(String)) dt.Columns.Add("Amount", GetType(Long)) dt.Columns.Add("IsNoData", GetType(Boolean))
' Pass args into General_Member_lists Dim lsDimMbrs As List(Of String) = BR_GeneralMemberLists.GetFilteredDataRows(si,globals,api,args) If lsDimMbrs.Count = 0 Then Return Nothing ' For each row header returned, get the amount for 13 months and write into dictionary of memberScript as key and amount as value Dim sTime As String = "" Dim sMbrScript As String = "" Dim cell As DataCell For Each sDims As String In lsDimMbrs 'Get and store FY amts For i As Integer = 1 To 12 sTime = $"T#{iWFYear}M{i}" sMbrScript = sDataBufferPOVScript & ":" & sTime & ":" & sDims cell = api.Data.GetDataCell(sMbrScript) If cell.CellStatus.ExistenceType.ToString = "NoData" Then dt.Rows.Add(sMbrScript, cell.CellAmount, True) Else dt.Rows.Add(sMbrScript, cell.CellAmount, False) End If 'BRapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, $"sMbrScript = {sMbrScript} || amt = {cell.CellAmount} || cell.CellStatus = {cell.CellStatus.ExistenceType.ToString}" ) Next 'Get and store carryover amt sTime = $"T#{iWFYear+1}M12" sMbrScript = sDataBufferPOVScript & ":" & sTime & ":" & sDims cell = api.Data.GetDataCell(sMbrScript) If cell.CellStatus.ExistenceType.ToString = "NoData" Then dt.Rows.Add(sMbrScript, cell.CellAmount, True) Else dt.Rows.Add(sMbrScript, cell.CellAmount, False) End If Next
If sScriptAmtCacheName <> "" Then BRApi.Utilities.SetSessionDataTable(si, si.UserName, sScriptAmtCacheName, dt)
Return lsDimMbrs Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function #End Region
#Region "GetPackageDetailsTarget" Public Function GetPackageDetailsTarget(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As List(Of String) Try Dim lsMasterDimList As New List( Of String) Dim sCacheString As String = "" Dim sCacheName As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("CacheName").Trim lsMasterDimList = BR_GeneralMemberLists.GetFilteredDataRows(si,globals,api,args)
sCacheString = BRApi.Utilities.GetWorkspaceSessionSetting(si, si.UserName, "FilteredDataRows", sCacheName,"")
Dim lsSubDimList As List(Of String) = sCacheString.Split(",").ToList()
lsMasterDimList = lsMasterDimList.except(lsSubDimList).ToList()
Return lsMasterDimList Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function #End Region
End Class

Try Select Case args.FunctionName Case args.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("BUDControlsEntityFilter") Return Me.BUDControlsEntityFilter(si, globals, api, args) Case args.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("BUDDashboardsToRedraw") Return Me.BUDDashboardsToRedraw(si, globals, api, args) Case args.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("BUDReportSubConsolidateTime") Return #Region "BUDDashboardsToRedraw: BUDDashboardsToRedraw" Public Function BUDDashboardsToRedraw(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As Object, ByVal args As DashboardStringFunctionArgs) As String Try Dim wfProfileName As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).Name Dim x As Integer = InStr(wfProfileName, ".") Dim sProfileName As String = wfProfileName.Substring(x + 0) 'BRAPI.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sProfileName) Dim sLRDashboard As String = "BUDPRO_BUDLDB_0__ReviewBUDDetails" 'Dim ufr As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("UFR_Id")
If sProfileName = "Review Financials" Or sProfileName = "Validate Requirements" Or sProfileName = "Validate Requirements CMD" Then Return "BUDPRO_BUDVAL_0__Main" & "," & sLRDashboard
Else If sProfileName = "Formulate Requirements" Then Return "BUDPRO_BUDCRT_0__Main" & "," & sLRDashboard
Else If wfProfileName.XFContainsIgnoreCase("Manage") Then Return "BUDPRO_BUDMGT_0__Main" & "," & sLRDashboard
Else If sProfileName = "Review Requirements" Then Return "BUDPRO_BUDREV_0__Main" & "," & sLRDashboard
Else If sProfileName = "Rollover Requirements" Then Return "BUDPRO_BUDREV_0__Main" & "," & sLRDashboard
Else If wfProfileName.XFContainsIgnoreCase("Approve") Then Return "BUDPRO_BUDAPR_0__Main" & "," & sLRDashboard
End If Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex))
End Try Return Nothing End Function

#Region "BUDReportSubConsolidateTime: BUDReportSubConsolidateTime" 'Return 5 years Time for subconsolidate data management sequence for BUD Report Public Function BUDReportSubConsolidateTime(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As Object, ByVal args As DashboardStringFunctionArgs) As String Try
Dim sScenario As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("Scenario") Dim sReturnString As String = "" Dim iScenarioId As Integer = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si, dimTypeId.Scenario, sScenario) Dim iTime As Integer = BRApi.Finance.Scenario.GetWorkflowTime(si, iScenarioId)/1000000 For i As Integer = 0 To 4 Step 1 If i = 0 Then sReturnString = $"T#{iTime}" Else sReturnString = $"{sReturnString},T#{iTime + i}" End If Next 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, $"sReturnString = {sReturnString}") Return sReturnString Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex))
End Try
End Function

#Region "CategoryMemberList: Category Member List Function" Public Function CategoryMemberList(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As Object, ByVal args As DashboardStringFunctionArgs, ByVal sBUDEntity As String) As String Try 'Usage: 'XFBR(UFR_String_Helper,CategoryMemberList,sUFREntity=[|!prompt_cbx_UFRPRO_AAAAAA_0CaAa_FundCenter__Shared!|]) 'Purpose: Generate cube view column member list containing UFR Category Names for U5#UFR_Priority_Cat_01 to U5#UFR_Priority_Cat_15 'Created: 10/12/2023 by Ralph Hudack 'Updated: mm/dd/yyyy by <name> Modification: 'Updated EH 090424 RMW-1565 Changed to annual for PGM_C20XX If args.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("CategoryMemberList") Then Dim sWFCube = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim sWFScenario As String = ScenarioDimHelper.GetNameFromId(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey) Dim sWFYear As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetYearFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) Dim sBUDTime As String = sWFYear & "M12" Dim sIC As String = sBUDEntity Dim sCatNum As String ="" ' "01" 'Range is 01 to 15 Dim sCatNameMemberScript As String ="" 'Generated string for BRApi Get Data Cell for REQ_Priority_Cat_Name Dim sCatName As String ="" 'Category Name obtained from BRApi Get Data Cell for REQ_Priority_Cat_Name Dim sCategoryMemberList As String ="" 'Returned Value: Example A#REQ_Priority_Cat_Name:V#Periodic:U5#UFR_Priority_Cat_01:Name(1st Category), 'Loop 15 times for UFR_Priority_Cat_01 to UFR_Priority_Cat_15 For iCounter As Integer = 1 To 15 'Get Category Name and generate Category Member List If iCounter < 10 Then sCatNum = "0" & iCounter.ToString 'Add leading zero's for single digit integers. Ex 01 to 09 Else sCatNum = iCounter.ToString End If sCatNameMemberScript = "Cb#" & sWFCube & ":E#" & sBUDEntity & ":C#Local:S#" & sWFScenario & ":T#" & sBUDTime & ":V#Annotation:A#REQ_Priority_Cat_Name:F#None:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#UFR_Priority_Cat_" & sCatNum & ":U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" sCatName = BRApi.Finance.Data.GetDataCellUsingMemberScript(si, sWFCube, sCatNameMemberScript).DataCellEx.DataCellAnnotation 'BRapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "sCatName = " & sCatName) If Len(sCatName) > 0 Then 'Concatenate Category Member List ' sCategoryMemberList = sCategoryMemberList & ",A#REQ_Priority_Cat_Name:V#Periodic:I#" & sIC & ":U5#UFR_Priority_Cat_" & sCatNum & ":Name(" & sCatName & ")" sCategoryMemberList = sCategoryMemberList & ",A#REQ_Priority_Cat_Name:V#Periodic:U5#UFR_Priority_Cat_" & sCatNum & ":I#" & sIC &":Name(" & sCatName & ")" End If If iCounter = 1 And Len(sCatName) < 1 Then 'Missing UFR Weights in REQ_Priority_Cat_Weight so send back dummy value with embedded error message. Dim sErrorMessage As String = "A#REQ_Priority_Cat_Name:V#Periodic:U5#UFR_Priority_Category:Name(Missing PGM Weights. Contact PGM Manager.)" Return sErrorMessage End If Next 'BRapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"PriorityCategoryMemberList: ||sCatNameMemberScript=" & sCatNameMemberScript & " ||sCategoryMemberList=" & sCategoryMemberList & "||") Return sCategoryMemberList End If
Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try Return Nothing End Function #End Region

Dim sCube As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("Cube") 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": sEntitySelection=" & sEntitySelection) If sCube <> "" Then wfCube = sCube
Dim sScenarioName As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("Scenario") If sScenarioName <> "" Then wfScenarioName = sScenarioName
Dim sTimeName As String = wfScenarioName.Substring(5,4) Dim iYear As Integer = CInt(sTimeName) 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": sPGMSelection=" & sPGMSelection & " wfScenarioName=" & wfScenarioName & " wfTimeName=" & wfTimeName )
Dim Account As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("Account").Trim
Dim sACOM As String = BRapi.Finance.Entity.Text(si, BRapi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si,dimtype.Entity.Id, wfCube), 1, 0, 0) Dim sYOYPctLimitMbrScript As String = "Cb#" & wfCube & ":S#" & wfScenarioName & ":T#" & iWFYear & ":C#USD:E#" & sACOM & "_General" sYOYPctLimitMbrScript &= ":V#Periodic:A#" & Account & ":O#Forms:I#None:F#None:U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None"
Dim PrctLimit As Decimal = BRApi.Finance.Data.GetDataCellUsingMemberScript(si, wfCube, sYOYPctLimitMbrScript).DataCellEx.DataCell.CellAmount PrctLimit = Math.Round(PrctLimit, 1)
Return PrctLimit & "%"
End Function #End Region

#Region "DynamicU8: DynamicU8" '====================================================================================================================================================================== ' Return U8# according to passed in Cube View name and wf profile name '====================================================================================================================================================================== ' Usage: ' - CV: BUD_Funding_Month_Amt ' - Monthly Or Year Requested Amount, Row Overrides ' - In this instance, the method is used to return U8#Top to make the cell read-only for the Review Budgets workflow instead of having to create a separate CV '======================================================================================================================================================================
Public Function DynamicU8(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As Object, ByVal args As DashboardStringFunctionArgs) As String Dim wfProfileName As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).Name Dim sCV As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("CV") Dim sAccount As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("Account")
Select Case sCV Case "BUD_Funding_Month_Amt" If wfProfileName.XFContainsIgnoreCase("Review Budgets") Return "U8#Top" End If If (wfProfileName.XFContainsIgnoreCase("Formulate Bud") And sAccount = "REQ_Validated_Amt") Return "U8#Top" End If If wfProfileName.XFContainsIgnoreCase("Validate Bud") And sAccount = "REQ_Validated_Amt" Then Return Nothing If Not (wfProfileName.XFContainsIgnoreCase("Formulate") Or wfProfileName.XFContainsIgnoreCase("Approve") Or wfProfileName.XFContainsIgnoreCase("Validate"))Then Return "U8#Top"
Case "BUD_Base_Info_RO_ALT" If wfProfileName.XFContainsIgnoreCase("Review Financials") Return "None" Else Return "ReadOnlyAnnotation" End If End Select Return Nothing End Function #End Region
#Region "DynamicFormatting: DynamicFormatting" Public Function DynamicFormatting(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As Object, ByVal args As DashboardStringFunctionArgs) As String Dim wfProfileName As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).Name Dim sCV As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("CV")
Select Case sCV Case "BUD_Base_Info_RO_ALT" If Not wfProfileName.XFContainsIgnoreCase("Review Financials") Return "BackgroundColor = XFLightBlue3" Else Return "" End If End Select Return Nothing End Function #End Region
#Region "DynamicU8None: DynamicU8None" '====================================================================================================================================================================== ' Offer a new row if all amounts are removed from a requirement. The row is only editable in Formulate step. '====================================================================================================================================================================== ' Usage: ' - CV: BUD_Funding_Month_Amt ' - Key_None Row: Formatting and column override ' - In this instance, the method is used display a "none" row if the requirement is empty, but set it to read-only (U8#None -> U8#Top) if not in Formulate step '======================================================================================================================================================================
Public Function DynamicU8None(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As Object, ByVal args As DashboardStringFunctionArgs) As String '======================================================================================================================== ' DECLARATIONS '========================================================================================================================
'Context Dim wfProfileName As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).Name Dim wfCube As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim wfScenarioName As String = ScenarioDimHelper.GetNameFromId(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey) Dim wfScenarioId As Integer = ScenarioDimHelper.GetIdFromName(si, wfScenarioName)
'Divide by 1000000, because Time ID comes back as full length (e.g. 2024000000 instead of 2024) Dim wfStartTime As Integer = BRApi.Finance.Scenario.GetWorkflowStartTime(si, wfScenarioId)/1000000 Dim wfEndTime As Integer = BRApi.Finance.Scenario.GetWorkflowEndTime(si, wfScenarioId)/1000000
'Type = Member | Format (what is the function returning?) Dim sType As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("Type") 'POV = Everything except for time, which is pulled from workflow and extended to FYDP (five years out) Dim sPOV As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("POV")
'Pull amount from the data cell associated with each {{POV:T#<FYDP Year>}} Dim dataCell As New DataCellInfoUsingMemberScript Dim amt As New Decimal
'======================================================================================================================== ' LOGIC '========================================================================================================================
'Loop through POV for each FYDP Year (e.g. 2024-2028) For counter = wfStartTime To wfEndTime dataCell = BRApi.Finance.Data.GetDataCellUsingMemberScript(si, wfCube, sPOV & ":T#" & counter.ToString) amt = dataCell.DataCellEx.DataCell.CellAmount
'Hide row if there is an existing amount for the requirement If sType = "Format" And amt <> 0 Return "IsRowVisible = False" End If
'Set row to read-only if not in Formulate step (fringe case, should only happen if zero-dollar req is submitted) If sType = "Member" And Not wfProfileName.XFContainsIgnoreCase("Formulate Bud") Return "U8#Top" End If Next
'Will be visible and writeable if in Formulate step with no amount in the BUD for full FYDP Return Nothing
End Function #End Region
#Region "ExportReportMDEPFilterList: ExportReportMDEPFilterList" Public Function ExportReportMDEPFilterList(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As Object, ByVal args As DashboardStringFunctionArgs) As String Try
Dim sPEGFilteredList As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("PEGFilteredList") 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"sPEGFilteredList: " & sPEGFilteredList) If String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(sPEGFilteredList) Return "U2#PEG.Base" End If
Dim lPEGFilteredList As List(Of String) = sPEGFilteredList.Split(",").ToList Dim sMDEPFilter As String = ""
For Each PEG As String In lPEGFilteredList 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"PEG List Item: " & PEG) PEG = PEG.Trim() If String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(sMDEPFilter) Then sMDEPFilter = $"U2#{PEG}.Base" Else sMDEPFilter = $"{sMDEPFilter},U2#{PEG}.Base" End If Next 'EE, II 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"MDEP Filter: " & sMDEPFilter) Return sMDEPFilter
Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function #End Region
#Region "GetAccountTranslatedValue: Get Account Translated Value Function" Public Function GetAccountTranslatedValue(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As Object, ByVal args As DashboardStringFunctionArgs, _ ByVal sAccount As String, ByVal sTranslationCd As String, ByVal sFlow As String, ByVal sEntity As String) As String Try 'Purpose: Get the Annotation Value of an Account for a given BUD and either return that value or return a translated value depding on sTranslationCd. 'Usage Ex 1 Return the Annotation value - XFBR(UFR_String_Helper,GetAccountTranslatedValue,UFREntity=|!prompt_cbx_UFRPRO_AAAAAA_0CaAa_FundCenter__Shared!|, UFRFlow=|!prompt_cbx_UFRPRO_AAAAAA_UFRListByEntity__Shared!|,UFRAccount=REQ_Notification_Email_List,TranslationCd=) 'Usage Ex 2 Return M12 or .Base - XFBR(UFR_String_Helper,GetAccountTranslatedValue,UFREntity=|!prompt_cbx_UFRPRO_AAAAAA_0CaAa_FundCenter__Shared!|, UFRFlow=|!prompt_cbx_UFRPRO_AAAAAA_UFRListByEntity__Shared!|,UFRAccount=REQ_Recurring_Cost_Ind,TranslationCd=AllMnthsOrSep) 'Usage Ex 3 Return :None or :U8#ReadOnlyAnnotation - XFBR(UFR_String_Helper,GetAccountTranslatedValue,UFREntity=|!prompt_cbx_UFRPRO_AAAAAA_0CaAa_FundCenter__Shared!|, UFRFlow=|!prompt_cbx_UFRPRO_AAAAAA_UFRListByEntity__Shared!|,UFRAccount=REQ_Request_Manpower_Ind,TranslationCd=WriteOrReadText)
Dim sCube = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim sScenario As String = ScenarioDimHelper.GetNameFromId(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey) Dim sYear As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetYearFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) Dim sTime As String = sYear & "M12" Dim sReturnValue As String = ""
'Get Annotation Value of Account member Dim sMemberScript As String = "Cb#" & sCube & ":E#" & sEntity & ":C#Local:S#" & sScenario & ":T#" & sTime & ":V#Annotation:A#" & sAccount &":F#" & sFlow & ":O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim sAccountValue As String = BRApi.Finance.Data.GetDataCellUsingMemberScript(si, sCube, sMemberScript).DataCellEx.DataCellAnnotation 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "sTranslationCd: --" & sTranslationCd & "--sMemberScript: --" & sMemberScript & "--" & "sAccountValue: --" & sAccountValue & "--") 'Determine whether to do a transformation or just return the If(Not String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(sTranslationCd)) Then 'Perform a Translation of the REQ_Recurring_Cost_Ind Annotation Value. 'Valid Values: WriteOrReadText, WriteOrReadNumber, AllMnthsOrSep, <More will be added in future. If (sAccount = "REQ_Recurring_Cost_Ind" And sTranslationCd = "AllMnthsOrSep") Then 'Translate the No/Yes value of REQ_Recurring_Cost_Ind: If Yes, return ".Base" Otherwise, return "M12" sReturnValue = "M12" 'Default to single month M12 If sAccountValue = "Yes" sReturnValue = ".Base" End If End If If (sTranslationCd = "WriteOrReadText" Or sTranslationCd = "WriteOrReadNumber") Then 'Get REQ_Workflow_Status and the Workflow type (Create, Review...), Get User's Group (Stakeholder, Analyst, Manger) 'RH 9/1/2023 Add logic below 'If REQ_Workflow_Status <> Working AND the signed on User does NOT belong to a Manager (g_UFR_*_MG_*) security group, sReturnValue = ":U8#ReadOnlyAnnotation" , Else sReturnValue = ":U8#None" ' If sAccountValue = "Yes" ' 'Enable Write Access to Account Member ' sReturnValue = "U8#None" ' End If
'Set Default to be "Read Only". Only the UFR Manager can edit the Cube View if Account REQ_Workflow_Status = "Working" 'RH 9/1/2023 Test using hardcoded: sReturnValue = "U8#ReadOnlyAnnotation" If (sTranslationCd = "WriteOrReadText") Then sReturnValue = "U8#ReadOnlyAnnotation" Else If (sTranslationCd = "WriteOrReadNumber") Then sReturnValue = "O#Top" Else sReturnValue = "U8#None" End If End If Else 'sTranslationCd is blank so return the Account Annotation Value sReturnValue = sAccountValue End If
'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "sAccount: --" & sAccount & "--" & "sReturnValue: --" & sReturnValue & "--" ) Return sReturnValue
Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function
#End Region
#Region "GetAnnotationDetail: Get Annotation Detail" 'Updated EH 8/29/24 RMW-1565 Updated wfTime to Annual Public Function GetAnnotationDetail(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As Object, ByVal args As DashboardStringFunctionArgs) As String Try Dim wfProfileName As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).Name Dim wfCube = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim wfScenario As String = ScenarioDimHelper.GetNameFromId(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey) Dim wfScenarioTypeID As Integer = BRApi.Finance.Scenario.GetScenarioType(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey).Id Dim wfTime As String = BRApi.Finance.Time.GetNameFromId(si,si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) & "M12" Dim WFYear As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetYearFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) Dim WFMonth As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetMonthIdFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) Dim BUDTime As String = WFYear & "M12" Dim BUDEntity As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("Entity") Dim BUDFlow As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("Flow")
If String.IsNullOrEmpty(BUDEntity) Or String.IsNullOrEmpty(BUDFlow) Then BUDEntity = ParseBUDEntity(si, globals, api, args) BUDFlow = ParseBUDFlow(si, globals, api, args) End If
Dim comments As String = ""
'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "entitiy " & BUDEntity) 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "flow " & BUDFlow) 'Get Annotaion detail. Attachement Type 300 Dim sql = "SELECT Text, CreatedUserName, CreatedTimestamp, LastEditedUserName, LastEditedTimestamp From DataAttachment with (NOLOCK) WHERE Cube = '" & wfCube & "'" & " and Entity = '" & BUDEntity & "'" & " and Scenario = '" & wfScenario & "'" & " and Flow = '" & BUDFlow & "'" & " and Time = '" & BUDTime & "'" & " and Account = 'REQ_Comments' and Origin = 'BeforeAdj' and IC = 'None' and UD1 = 'None' and UD2 = 'None' and UD3 = 'None' and UD4 = 'None' and UD5 = 'None' and UD6 = 'None' and UD7 = 'None' and UD8 = 'None' and AttachmentType = '300' ORDER BY CreatedTimestamp" 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "sql: " & sql) Dim dtComments As DataTable = New DataTable("comments") Using dbConnApp As DBConnInfo = BRAPi.Database.CreateApplicationDbConnInfo(si) dtComments = BRApi.Database.ExecuteSql(dbConnApp, sql, False) End Using
For Each rw As DataRow In dtComments.Rows comments = vbCrLf & "Created by: " & rw.Item("CreatedUserName") & " (" & rw.Item("CreatedTimestamp") & ")" _ & " - " & "Updated by: " & rw.Item("LastEditedUserName") & " (" & rw.Item("LastEditedTimestamp") & ")" _ & vbCrLf & rw.Item("Text") _ & vbCrLf & comments Next 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "c: " & comments) Return comments Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function #End Region
#Region "GetApprovalAccount: Get Approval Account" Public Function GetApprovalAccount(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As Object, ByVal args As DashboardStringFunctionArgs) As String Try Dim wfProfileName As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).Name 'Dim wfLevel As String = wfProfileName.Substring(0,2) Dim wfCube = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim sEntity As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("Entity") Dim ApprovalAccount As String = "A#REQ_Allow_Approval" '& wfLevel If sEntity.XFContainsIgnoreCase("General") Then sEntity = sEntity.Replace("_General","") End If Dim DimPK As DimPk = brapi.Finance.Dim.GetDimPk(si, "E_" & wfCube) If brapi.Finance.Members.HasChildren(si,DimPk,brapi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si,dimtype.Entity.Id,sEntity)) Then Return ApprovalAccount Else Return "A#REQ_Allow_Approval:Name(Ignore):U8#ReadOnlyAnnotation" End If Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function #End Region 'removed WFlevel and not being used
#Region "getBUDAnnotation: Get BUD Annotation Function" 'Get BUD Annotation using Dim infos Public Function getBUDAnnotation(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As Object, ByVal args As DashboardStringFunctionArgs, _ ByVal sAccount As String, ByVal sFlow As String, ByVal sEntity As String, ByVal sCube As String, ByVal sScenario As String, ByVal sTime As String, ByVal sIC As String, Optional sU5 As String = "None",Optional sU8 As String = "None") As String Try Dim sMemberScript As String = "" If sAccount.XFContainsIgnoreCase("Stkhldr") Then sMemberScript = "Cb#" & sCube & ":E#" & sEntity & ":C#Local:S#" & sScenario & ":T#" & sTime & ":V#Annotation:A#" & sAccount & ":F#" & sFlow & ":O#BeforeAdj:I#" & sIC & ":U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#" & sU5 & ":U6#None:U7#None:U8#" & sU8
Else 'Get annotations to return sMemberScript = "Cb#" & sCube & ":E#" & sEntity & ":C#Local:S#" & sScenario & ":T#" & sTime & ":V#Annotation:A#" & sAccount & ":F#" & sFlow & ":O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#" & sU5 & ":U6#None:U7#None:U8#" & sU8 End If Dim BUDAnnotationCell As DataCellInfoUsingMemberScript = BRApi.Finance.Data.GetDataCellUsingMemberScript(si, sCube, sMemberScript) Dim BUDAnnotation As String = BUDAnnotationCell.DataCellEx.DataCellAnnotation
'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,$"sAccount = {sAccount} || sFlow = {sFlow} || sEntity = {sEntity} || sCube = {sCube} || sScenario = {sScenario} || sTime = {sTime} || sIC = {sIC} || sU5 = {sU5} || sU8 = {sU8} ||BUDAnnotation = {BUDAnnotation}")
